223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22traders%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f573379e6ff30001d4e7631%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20pandemic%20and%20the%20rise%20of%20AI%20have%20brought%20about%20a%20new%20era%20for%20investors%2C%20according%20to%20BlackRock%20strategist%20Helen%20Jewell.%3Cp%3EMario%20Tama%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20pandemic%20has%20ushered%20in%20a%20new%20era%20for%20investing%2C%20according%20to%20BlackRock.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETraders%20will%20focus%20above%20all%20else%20on%20beating%20the%20market%2C%20Helen%20Jewell%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEarnings%20and%20other%20stock%20specifics%20will%20likely%20reign%20supreme%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWelcome%20to%20a%20new%20era%20of%20investing%2C%20where%20%26quot%3Bpicking%20winners%26quot%3B%20matters%20above%20anything%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20view%20being%20put%20forward%20by%20BlackRock's%20Helen%20Jewell%2C%20who%20told%20Insider%20Wednesday%20that%20the%20pandemic%20had%20brought%20an%20end%20to%20the%20post-financial%20crisis%20%26quot%3Beasy%20money%26quot%3B%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20real%20opportunity%20for%20stock-picking%20and%20within%20that%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Falpha%5C%22%3Ealpha%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20amount%20by%20which%20a%20trader%20is%20able%20to%20beat%20a%20benchmark%20index%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fs%26amp%3Bp_500%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20you%20saw%20for%20a%20long%20period%20of%20time%20was%20styles%20driving%20returns%E2%80%A6%20but%20now%20what%20we're%20starting%20to%20see%20come%20back%20in%20are%20stock%20specifics%2C%20and%20particularly%20earnings%2C%26quot%3B%20Jewell%2C%20who's%20the%20CIO%20of%20BlackRock's%20Fundamental%20Equities%20group%20for%20Europe%2C%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20and%20Africa%2C%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStocks%20racked%20up%20year%20after%20year%20of%20solid%20gains%20between%202008%20and%202021%2C%20powered%20higher%20by%20historically%20low%20interest%20rates%20across%20the%20western%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2018%20months%20ago%2C%20central%20banks%20started%20to%20rapidly%20lift%20borrowing%20costs%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20clamp%20down%20on%20inflation%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0and%20that's%20sparked%20a%20massive%20surge%20in%20volatility%20in%20both%20US%20and%20European%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20in%202023%2C%20a%20group%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Ftech-stocks-tesla-nvidia-apple-microsoft-amazon-the-magnificent-seven-2023-6%5C%22%3Emega-cap%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BMagnificent%20Seven%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20seen%20their%20share%20prices%20soar%20thanks%20to%20the%20rise%20of%20AI%20%E2%80%93%20but%20stocks%20from%20other%20sectors%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fsvb-silicon-valley-bank-collapse-jpmorgan-morgan-stanley-bank-stocks-2023-3%5C%22%3Efinancials%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fdereksaul%2F2023%2F07%2F03%2Fworst-stocks-of-2023s-first-half-battered-banks-and-vaccine-makers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epharmaceuticals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20plunged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJewell%20sees%20the%20uncertainty%20of%20the%20past%20two%20years%20as%20a%20transition%20period%20into%20a%20new%20era%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0one%20that%20she%20believes%20will%20be%20defined%20by%20high%20but%20stable%20interest%20rates%20and%20the%20return%20of%20alpha%20as%20a%20golden%20metric%20for%20active%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20what%20we're%2