0documentaries%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20hippie%20and%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eglassblowing%20culture%2C%20and%20I%20learned%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic1.squarespace.com%2Fstatic%2F5817e1cf725e2564c2cd09fb%2Ft%2F591349f42e69cf6b22af8750%2F1494436350917%2FChihuly%2BSurvey-Full%2BStudy-Final.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEugene%20has%20a%20large%20glass-blowing%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20that%20I'd%20be%20able%20to%20fit%20right%20in%20because%20I'd%20always%20thought%20of%20myself%20as%20a%20hippie.%20However%2C%20that%20was%20not%20the%20case.%20When%20I%20got%20here%2C%20I%20was%20overwhelmed%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.census.gov%2Fquickfacts%2Ffact%2Ftable%2Feugenecityoregon%2FRHI225222%23RHI225222%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20lack%20of%20diversity%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20prevalence%20of%20cultural%20appropriation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20glaring%20examples%20of%20appropriation%20can%20be%20found%20in%20the%20reggae%20scene.%20White%20artists%2C%20born%20and%20raised%20in%20Eugene%2C%20make%20good%20livings%20performing%20in%20fake%20Jamaican%20accents%2C%20and%20are%20held%20in%20high%20esteem%20amongst%20the%20community.%20I've%20pointed%20this%20out%20many%20times%2C%20but%20my%20thoughts%20aren't%20considered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20it's%20like%20to%20live%20in%20Oregon%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20arrived%20in%20Oregon%2C%20I%20experienced%20a%20serious%20culture%20shock.%20Oregon%2C%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20offered%20much%20of%20what%20I%20sought%20and%20desired.%20But%20the%20absence%20of%20diversity%2C%20particularly%20Black%20and%20African%20communities%2C%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20unrelenting%20stares%20and%20intrusive%20questioning%20made%20me%20feel%20unsafe%20and%20unwanted%20within%20the%20community.%20I've%20experienced%20racism%20and%20gaslighting%20almost%20daily%20since%20I%20arr