0in%20regard%20to%20affordability%20and%20stress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20I%20enjoy%20most%20about%20Oregon%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20constant%20racism%2C%20I've%20managed%20to%20cultivate%20an%20appreciation%20for%20Eugene's%20simplicity.%20I%20enjoy%20the%20laid-back%20attitude%20of%20the%20Pacific%20Northwest.%20People%20here%20aren't%20consumed%20with%20fashion%20and%20high-cost%20brands.%20That's%20not%20to%20say%20you%20won't%20see%20them%2C%20but%20simply%20having%20a%20Gucci%20bag%20isn't%20seen%20as%20a%20status%20symbol%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjobs.nike.com%2Fwhq%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ethis%20is%20near%20Nike's%20headquarters%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it's%20not%20uncommon%20to%20see%20ultrarare%20Jordans%20at%20local%20dive%20bars.%20But%20generally%2C%20those%20people%20are%20collectors%20and%20not%20as%20obsessed%20with%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20met%20my%20future%20wife%2C%20who's%20from%20Oregon%2C%20in%202017%20and%20married%20her%20two%20years%20later.%20I%20can%20say%20with%20certainty%20that%2C%20for%20me%2C%20it%20was%20love%20at%20first%20sight.%20Since%20moving%20here%2C%20I've%20enrolled%20in%20college%2C%20and%20I'm%20a%20few%20terms%20away%20from%20earning%20my%20journalism%20degree%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Oregon.%20I've%20found%20an%20incredible%20set%20of%20advisors%20and%20supporters%20in%20the%20university%20space%2C%20which%20has%20allowed%20me%20to%20thrive%20as%20a%20returning%20student.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chandlor%20Henderson%20with%20wife%20Alison%20Helzer.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64effe2a5cb621001989fe81%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHenderson%20with%20wife%20Alison.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Chandlor%20Henderson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20also%20been%20a%20mentor%20helping%20young%20Black%20men%20navigate%20a%20sometimes%20hostile%20environment%20and%20feel%20pride%20in%20their%20heritage.%20This%20is%20work%20I'm%20incredibly%20proud%20of%2C%20and%20I'll%20miss%20it%20tremendously%20when%20I%20leave%20the%20West%20Coast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20I'm%20leaving%20Oregon%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foregon-measure-110-live-vote-count-results-2020%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EOregon's%20progressive%20stance%20on%20drug%20decriminalization%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20commendable%2C%20it%20has%20inadvertently%20spawned%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F07%2F31%2Fhealth%2Fportland-oregon-drugs.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ea%20disconcerting%20culture%20of%20drug%20use%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Combined%20with%20a%20lack%20of%20mental-health%20resources%2C%20drug%20abuse%20is%20wreaking%20havoc%20on%20this%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eugene-or.gov%2F3470%2FHomelessness%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20effect%20is%20visible%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I've%20seen%20people%20shooting%20up%20on%20the%20sidewalk%20in%20broad%20daylight.%20I've%20been%20offered%20hard%20drugs%20on%20many%20occasions.%20And%20it's%20not%20uncommon%20to%20see%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oregonlive.com%2Fportland%2F2019%2F06%2Fportland-has-a-plan-for-its-human-poop-problem.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeople%20defecating%20in%20public%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oregonlive.com%2Feducation%2F2022%2F10%2Foregon-school-performance-craters-relative-to-national-averages-elementary-and-middle-school-math-scores-rank-6th-worst-in-us.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ethe%20state's%20subpar%20ranking%20in%20public%20education%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20makes%20me%20apprehensive%20about%20raising%20my%20f