h%20competitors%20including%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finvestor.dennys.com%2Fnews%2Fnews-details%2F2023%2FDennys-Corporation-Reports-Results-For-Second-Quarter-2023%2Fdefault.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDenny's%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finvestor.cbrlgroup.com%2Fnews-releases%2Fnews-release-details%2Fcracker-barrel-reports-third-quarter-fiscal-2023-results%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECracker%20Barrel%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chain's%20new%20biscuit%20lineup%20includes%20a%20breakfast%20biscuit%20sandwich%2C%20a%20chicken%20biscuit%20sandwich%2C%20a%20strawberries-and%20cream%20biscuit%2C%20and%20biscuits%20and%20gravy.%20The%20biscuits%20are%20sold%20as%20combo%20plates%20or%20a%20la%20carte.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKieran%20Donahue%2C%20the%20chain's%20chief%20marketing%20officer%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20adding%20biscuits%20was%20part%20of%20the%20chain's%20goal%20to%20offer%20diners%20%26quot%3Bcraveable%20and%20flavorful%26quot%3B%20items%20any%20time%20of%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20set%20out%20to%20see%20whether%20they%20were%20craveable%20during%20a%20Monday%20visit%2C%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20national%20launch.%20I'm%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20biscuit%20snob%2C%20having%20tried%20some%20of%20the%20best%20biscuits%20in%20the%20US%2C%20including%20the%20biscuits%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lovelesscafe.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELoveless%20Cafe%20in%20Nashville%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Tennessee%2C%20and%20the%20tiny%20biscuits%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcalliesbiscuits.com%2F%3F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECallie's%20Hot%20Little%20Biscuit%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Charleston%2C%20South%20Carolina.%20I%20even%20went%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ocregister.com%2F2011%2F10%2F23%2Fmy-morning-as-a-carls-jr-biscuit-maker%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebehind%20the%20scenes%20at%20Carl's%20Jr.%3C%2Fa%3E%20years%20ago%20to%20learn%20how%20it%20made%20its%20scratch%20biscuits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20think%20I%20can%20spot%20a%20good%20biscuit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20I%20discovered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20ordered%20the%20breakfast%20biscuit%20sandwich%2C%20a%20chicken%20biscuit%20sandwich%2C%20the%20strawberries-and-cream%20biscuit%2C%20a%20buttermilk%20biscuit%20with%20gravy%2C%20and%20a%20plain%20biscuit%20with%20butter.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IHOP%20Biscuit%20Menu-%20all%20four%20items%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ee13708f9177001939feb5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20IHOPs%20in%20my%20town%20have%20shut%20down.%20The%20closest%20restaurant%20to%20my%20home%20was%202%20miles%20away%2C%20in%20Santa%20Ana%2C%20California.%20It%20was%20next%20to%20a%20McDonald's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20restaurant%20was%20empty%20at%205%20p.m.%20I%20was%20seated%20by%20a%20friendly%20server%20who%20handed%20me%20a%20standard%20menu%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20laminated%20menu%20promoting%20the%20new%20biscuit%20lineup.%20She%20was%20very%20helpful%20and%20answered%20all%20of%20my%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20first%20thing%20I%20noticed%20as%20I%20scoured%20the%20menu%20was%20the%20wide%20range%20of%20prices%20for%20the%20various%20biscuit%20offerings%2C%20from%20%244%20for%20an%20a%20la%20carte%20biscuit%20with%20butter%20to%20%2415.50%20for%20the%20chicken%20biscuit%20sandwich%2C%20which%20comes%20with%20one%20side%20dish.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IHOP%20Biscuit%20laminated%20menu%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ee153b8f917700193a0098%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20stunned%20by%20the%20%2415.50%20price%20tag%20of%20the%20chicken%20biscuit%20sandwich.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20maybe%20it%20came%20with%20two%20side%20dishes%2C%20but%20it%20comes%20with%C2%A0a%20choice%20of%20only%20one%20of%20the%20following%3A%20hash%20browns%2C%20french%20fries%2C%20two%20buttermilk%20pancakes%2C%20or%20fresh%20fruit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20started%20with%20the%20breakfast%20biscuit%20sandwich.%20The%20biscuit%20was%20much%20bigger%20than%20I'd%20expected%20and%20flatter.%20It%20looked%20more%20like%20an%20English%20muffin%20than%20a%20fluffy%20biscuit.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IHOP%20Breakfast%20Sandwich%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ee16669664cf0019e834b0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAfter%20the%20%247%20deal%20ends%20on%20September%2027%2C%20IHOP%20said%20pricing%20on%20the%20breakfast%20biscuit%20sandwich%20would%20vary.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hefty%20breakfast%20sandwich%20is%20stuffed%20with%20two%20fried%20eggs%2C%20a%20slice%20of%20American%20cheese%2C%20two%20strips%20of%20hickory-smoked%20bacon%2C%20and%20cheese%20sauce.%20It's%20served%20with%20a%20choice%20of%20two%20buttermilk%20pancakes%2C%20hash%20browns%2C%20or%20seasonal%20fresh%20fruit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20the%20hash%20browns.%3Cu%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biscuit%20had%20a%20dark-brown%20top%20and%20was%20shaped%20like%20a%20disc.%20The%20fluffy%20center%20was%20missing.%20If%20you're%20a%20cheese%20fan%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20like%20this%20meal%2C%20as%20the%20cheese%20sauce%20gave%20the%20sandwich%20an%20extra-savory%20kick.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20September%2026%2C%20IHOP%20is%20offering%20the%20breakfast%20biscuit%20sandwich%20with%20a%20side%20for%20%247.%C2%A0%20At%20that%20price%2C%20it's%20a%20steal%20of%20a%20deal%20for%20a%20full-service-dining%20breakfast%20meal.%20Having%20tried%20a%20few%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwendys-vs-mcdonalds-which-chain-has-the-best-breakfast-2023-8%5C%22%3Ebreakfast%20meals%20at%20McDonald's%20recently%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20would%20recommend%20this%20meal%20deal%20for%20takeout.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20far%20superior%20to%20the%20McDonald's%20offerings%20and%20cheaper.%20McDonald's%20charges%20%248.60%20for%20a%20bacon%2C%20egg%2C%20and%20cheese%20biscuit%20meal%20that%20includes%20a%20hash%20brown%20and%20a%20beverage%2C%20according%20to%20the%20McDonald's%20app.%20(The%20search%20was%20in%20Orange%2C%20California%2C%20so%20pricing%20may%20vary%20elsewhere.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPro%20tip%3A%20The%20breakfast%20sandwich%20is%20advertised%20as%20coming%20with%20two%20fried%20eggs.%20But%20I%20learned%20you%20could%20order%20the%20sandwich%20with%20any%20egg%20style.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IHOP%20breakfast%20biscuit%20sandwich%20comes%20with%20eggs%20of%20your%20choice%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ee22cc8f917700193a10b0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20ordered%20the%20breakfast%20sandwich%2C%20the%20server%20asked%20me%20how%20I%20would%20like%20my%20eggs%20cooked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20for%20fried%20eggs%20cooked%20over%20medium%20for%20a%20slightly%20runny%20egg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20egg%20was%20cooked%20perfectly%2C%20and%20I%20enjoyed%20having%20a%20choice%20of%20egg%20preparation%20%E2%80%94%20a%20perk%20not%20offered%20at%20fast-food%20restaurants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20chicken%20biscuit%20sandwich%20was%20a%20four-napkin%20adventure%20that%20ultimately%20required%20me%20to%20use%20a%20steak%20knife.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221804%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IHOP%20Chicken%20Biscuit%20Sandwich%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ee1eb69664cf0019e83eed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221353%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20innovative%20savory%20biscuit%20sandwich%20comes%20layered%20with%20a%20buttermilk%20fried%20chicken%20breast%2C%20hash%20browns%2C%20pickle%20chips%2C%20and%20country%20gravy.%20It%20comes%20with%20a%20choice%20of%20french%20fries%2C%20onion%20rings%2C%20fresh%20fruit%2C%20two%20buttermilk%20pancakes%2C%20or%20side%20salad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20the%20fries.%C2%A0%3Cu%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20%2415.50%2C%20this%20meal%20comes%20with%20high%20expectations%2C%20and%20it%20failed%20miserably.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sandwich%20is%20served%20with%20a%20steak%20knife%2C%20and%20after%20taking%20my%20first%20bite%2C%20I%20could%20see%20why.%20The%20hash%20browns%20and%20country%20gravy%20fused%2C%20making%20for%20a%20savory%20paste%20that%20caused%20the%20sandwich%20to%20fall%20apart%20after%20one%20bite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20needed%20several%20napkins%20to%20wipe%20my%20fingers%20and%20mouth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20forked%20and%20knifed%20it%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20way.%20I%20love%20pickles%2C%20but%20I%20couldn't%20taste%20them.%20The%20tiny%20chips%20were%20smashed%20inside%20the%20biscuit%20under%20a%20gooey%20mixture%20of%20gravy%20and%20hash%20browns.%20The%20fried%20chicken%20was%20greasy%20and%20thin%20on%20meat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20it%20was%20a%20tasty%20concoction.%20I%20give%20the%20culinary%20team%20at%20IHOP%20kudos%20for%20mixing%20gravy%20with%20hash%20browns.%20But%20despite%20being%20quite%20tasty%2C%20it%20was%20a%20messy%2C%20overpriced%20sandwich.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI'm%20not%20a%20fan%20of%20biscuits%20and%20gravy%2C%20but%20I%20liked%20the%20approach%20IHOP%20made%20with%20this%20dish%20because%20the%20biscuit%20wasn't%20slathered%20in%20it.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IHOP%20Biscuits%20and%20Gravy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ee245f8f917700193a12e3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biscuits-and-gravy%20dish%20is%20advertised%20on%20the%20menu%20as%20a%20%2413.50%20combo%20meal%20that%20comes%20with%20two%20eggs%2C%20two%20pork-sausage%20links%2C%20two%20hickory-smoked%20bacon%20strips%2C%20and%20hash%20browns.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20want%20that%20much%20food%2C%20so%20I%20asked%20whether%20I%20could%20order%20the%20item%20a%20la%20carte.%20I%20was%20able%20to%20get%20one%20biscuit%20with%20gravy%20for%20%245.%20The%20biscuit%20was%20able%20to%20shine%20a%20bit%20more%20on%20this%20dish%20because%20it%20wasn't%20saturated%20with%20thick%20gravy.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20call%20this%20gravy.%20It%20was%20more%20like%20a%20tangy%2C%20country-style%20white%20sauce.%20It%20definitely%20seemed%20a%20bit%20%26quot%3Bwatered%26quot%3B%20down%2C%20which%20would%20probably%20offend%20aficionados%20of%20Southern%20gravy.%20But%20I%20liked%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20a%20la%20carte%20buttermilk%20biscuit%20was%20saturated%20in%20butter%20and%20looked%20like%20it%20had%20been%20toasted%20on%20a%20flattop%20grill.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221673%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IHOP%20plain%20biscuit%20-%20new%20biscuit%20menu%20debuts%20August%2028%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ee28a39664cf0019e84adc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221254%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ordered%20the%20biscuit%20a%20la%20carte%20so%20I%20could%20get%20a%20better%20taste%20of%20the%20biscuit%20without%20any%20other%20ingredients.%20I%20ordered%20it%20with%20a%20side%20of%20butter%2C%20which%20was%20completely%20unnecessary%20because%20the%20biscuit%20was%20already%20saturated%20with%20it.%20It%20was%20very%20greasy.%20They%20must%20be%20toasting%20it%20on%20a%20flattop%20grill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biscuit%20is%20flaky%2C%20but%20it%20didn't%20look%20like%20a%20biscuit.%20It%20looks%20like%20an%20English%20muffin%20and%20even%20had%20the%20nooks%20and%20crannies%20of%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20best%20item%20came%20last.%20The%20strawberries-and-cream%20biscuit%20tasted%20like%20a%20strawberry%20biscuit%20shortcake%20%E2%80%94%20crazy%20good.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IHOP%20Strawberry%20and%20Cream%20Biscuit%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ee2ba59664cf0019e84e40%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20most%20beautiful%20presentation%20of%20all%20the%20dishes.%20It%20came%20close%20to%20looking%20like%20the%20picture%20on%20the%20menu%2C%20except%20it%20could%20have%20used%20a%20lot%20more%20strawberries.%20I%20ordered%20the%20a%20la%20carte%20buttermilk%20biscuit%2C%20which%20is%20split%20and%20filled%20with%20cheesecake%20mousse%2C%20sliced%20strawberries%2C%20a%20drizzle%20of%20syrup%2C%20a%20sugary%20whipped%20topping%2C%20and%20powdered%20sugar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Canada%2C%20they%20use%20biscuits%20instead%20of%20sponge%20cakes%20to%20make%20strawberry%20shortcakes.%20I%20learned%20this%20from%20my%20many%20trips%20to%20Prince%20Edward%20Island%2C%20the%20location%20of%20my%20husband's%20family%20home.%20This%20dish%20reminded%20me%20of%20the%20many%20biscuit%20shortcakes%20I'd%20eaten%20while%20visiting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cheesecake%20mouse%20and%20syrup%20elevated%20the%20dish.%20I%20would%20recommend%20ordering%20this%20as%20a%20dessert%20for%20lunch%20or%20dinner.%20But%20it%20could%20also%20work%20as%20a%20sweet%20breakfast%20meal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20trouble%20I%20had%20with%20the%20dish%20was%20that%20I%20didn't%20know%20how%20to%20tackle%20it.%20I%20tried%20to%20cut%20it%20in%20half%2C%20but%20it%20fell%20apart%2C%20as%20the%20biscuit%20was%20very%20thick%20and%20doughy.%20Finally%2C%20I%20just%20used%20the%20side%20of%20my%20fork%20to%20cut%20my%20way%20into%20each%20piece%2C%20like%20I%20was%20eating%20a%20piece%20of%20cake%20or%20pie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20dish%20cost%20%247.50%20a%20la%20carte.%20As%20a%20combo%20dish%20served%20with%20two%20eggs%2C%20two%20strips%20of%20bacon%20or%20sausage%20links%2C%20and%20hash%20browns%2C%20it%20costs%20%2412.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOverall%2C%20the%20biscuit%20menu%20is%20good%20for%20IHOP%20fans%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20see%20this%20food%20strategy%20enticing%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20customers%20to%20patronize%20the%20pancake%20chain.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221196%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IHOP%20Chicken%20Biscuit%20Sandwich%20-%20review%20of%20new%20biscuit%20menu%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ee443e26dda200194d2ef4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22897%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIHOP%20has%20made%20efforts%20over%20the%20past%20several%20years%20to%20boost%20sales%20and%20lure%20new%20customers%20by%20introducing%20new%20foods%20to%20the%20menu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20famous%20marketing%20campaign%20came%20in%202018%2C%20when%20the%20chain%20said%20it%20would%20change%20its%20name%20to%20%26quot%3BIHOb%26quot%3B%20to%20showcase%20its%20new%20lineup%20of%20steak%20burgers.%20IHOP%20has%20been%20introducing%20menu%20items%20ever%20since%2C%20including%20burritos%20and%20bowls%20in%202021%20and%20sweet-and-savory%20crepes%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesswire.com%2Fnews%2Fhome%2F20230329005037%2Fen%2FIHOP%25C2%25AE-Introduces-Largest-Menu-Evolution-To-Date-with-New-Craveable-and-Flavorful-Lineup-Made-for-Any-Time-of-Day%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMarch%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20chain%20refreshed%20its%20eggs-Benedict%20dishes%20by%20adding%20a%20high-quality%20hollandaise%20sauce.%20It%20also%20put%20two%20new%20items%20on%20its%20Ultimate%20Steakburgers%20menu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20menu%2C%20the%20culinary%20team%20at%20IHOP%20has%20done%20a%20fine%20job%20introducing%20some%20solid%20biscuit%20creations.%20They%20are%20sure%20to%20excite%20existing%20customers.%20But%20I%20don't%20think%20this%20lineup%20is%20good%20enough%20to%20sway%20new%20people%20to%20give%20IHOP%20a%20chance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20visit%20was%20proof%20of%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20left%20with%20a%20bit%20of%20heartburn%20and%20a%20bit%20of%20heartache%20for%20the%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20at%20IHOP%20for%20more%20than%20an%20hour%20at%20dinnertime%2C%20and%20not%20a%20single%20other%20patron%20came%20in%20for%20dinner.%20The%20restaurant%20was%20sadly%20empty%20when%20I%20entered%20and%20after%20I%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fihop-new-disapointing-biscuit-menu-review-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693472400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ee399f2dfb7800199feb34%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fihop-new-disapointing-biscuit-menu-review-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Insider%20tried%20IHOP's%20new%20biscuit%20menu%2C%20which%20includes%20a%20breakfast%20biscuit%20sandwich%2C%20a%20strawberries-and-cream%20biscuit%2C%20and%20biscuits%20and%20gravy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nluna%40insider.com%2