ject%20Monitoring%20Division.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20a%20total%201%2C646%20projects%20under%20scanner%2C%20809%20projects%20(including%2098%20of%20railways)%20are%20delayed%20from%20their%20original%20scheduled%20dates%20of%20completion%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported%2C%20citing%20a%20July%202023%20report%20shared%20with%20the%20PMO%20and%20other%20wings%20of%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%20809%20projects%2C%20213%20projects%20(including%20nine%20of%20railways)%20are%20exceptionally%20delayed%2C%20leading%20to%20maximum%20cost%20overruns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelays%20in%20land%20acquisition%2C%20obtaining%20clearances%2C%20tendering%2C%20contractual%20issues%20and%20inadequate%20manpower%2C%20technical%20approvals%2C%20and%20law%20and%20order%20problems%20are%20the%20issues%20leading%20to%20the%20exceptional%20delay%20of%20these%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECost%20overruns%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20on%20August%201%2C%202023%2C%20the%20Ramganjmund-Bhopal%20rail%20line%20project%20of%20Western%20Railway%20has%20an%20estimated%20cost%20overrun%20of%20Rs%203%2C032%20crore.%20The%20project%20was%20sanctioned%20in%202002%20with%20an%20estimated%20cost%20of%20Rs%20425%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Udhampur-Srinagar-Baramulla%20rail%20line%20project%20has%20a%20cost%20overrun%20of%20Rs%2037%2C012%20crore.%20It%20was%20sanctioned%20in%201995%20at%20an%20original%20estimated%20budget%20of%20Rs%202%2C500%20crore.%20The%20project%20is%20delayed%20by%20more%20than%2021%20years%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lalitpur-Satna-Rewa%20Singruli%20project%E2%80%99s%20escalated%20budget%20has%20touched%20Rs%208%2C249%20crore.%20It%20was%20sanctioned%20in%201998%20with%20an%20original%20estimated%20cost%20of%20Rs%20248%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20BG%20rail%20line%20from%20Byrnihat%20to%20Shilong%2C%20sanctioned%20in%202010%20with%20an%20original%20budget%20of%20Rs%20906%20crore%2C%20is%20delayed%20w