%22%3E%E2%80%94%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0taking%20the%20volume%20shipped%20to%2022%20million%20cubic%20meters%2C%20per%20an%20analysis%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.globalwitness.org%2Fen%2Fpress-releases%2Feu-imports-russian-lng-have-jumped-40-invasion-ukraine%2F%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.globalwitness.org%2Fen%2Fpress-releases%2Feu-imports-russian-lng-have-jumped-40-invasion-ukraine%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3EGlobal%20Witness%2C%20a%20non-governmental%20organization%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0released%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20analysis%20used%20data%20from%20Kpler%2C%20a%20commodities%20data%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20EU%20bought%20over%20half%2C%20or%2052%25%2C%20of%20all%2041.6%20million%20cubic%20meters%20of%20LNG%20Russia%20exported%20this%20year%20%E2%80%94%20up%20from%2049%25%20and%2039%25%20in%202022%20and%202021%2C%20respectively%2C%20according%20to%20Global%20Witness'%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20big%20buyers%20of%20Russian%20LNG%20are%20China%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20South%20Korea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20EU's%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F1e70ff72-52d8-46b6-a8f4-fcc86fb88a6d%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0imports%20of%20Russian%20LNG%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0from%20January%20to%20July%20this%20year%20breached%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fmarkets%2Fcommodities%2Fglobal-lng-volumes-hit-record-high-europe-crowds-out-poorer-asia-russell-2023-01-12%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecord%20high%20last%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20meaning%20the%20bloc%20could%20be%20buying%20an%20unprecedented%20amount%20of%20the%20fuel%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGlobal%20Witness%20projects%20the%20EU's%20Russian%20LNG%20purchases%20in%202023%20to%20total%20nearly%205.3%20billion%20euros%2C%20or%20%245.75%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20EU%20used%20to%20import%20around%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.consilium.europa.eu%2Fen%2Finfographics%2Feu-gas-supply%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone-third%20of%20Russian%20piped%20gas%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20its%20energy%20needs.%20But%20it%20is%20now%20importing%20more%20LNG%20as%20most%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fdenmark-invites-nord-stream-operator-help-salvage-unidentified-object-2023-03-23%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERussian%20piped%20gas%20flows%20to%20the%20EU%3C%2Fa%3E%20via%20a%20%3Ca%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Frussia-not-resume-nord-stream-gas-flow-until-sanctions-lifted-2022-9%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22293fd9b6d51e5da43dce3aaa4d2a1214%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%22100%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Frussia-not-resume-nord-stream-gas-flow-until-sanctions-lifted-2022-9%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%3Ekey%20pipeline%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20halted%20after%20a%20major%20explosion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20there's%20a%20key%20reason%20why%20the%20bloc%20continues%20to%20snap%20up%20Russian%20LNG.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRussian%20LNG%20shipments%20continue%20to%20flow%20to%20EU%20countries%20at%20least%20in%20part%20due%20to%20long-term%20contracts%20that%20were%20signed%20long%20before%20the%20Russian%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20in%20February%202022%2C%26quot%3B%20Kpler%20analyst%20Adam%20Bennett%20told%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBennett%20added%20that%2090%25%20of%20Russian%20LNG%20flows%20into%20the%20EU%20went%20to%20Belgium%2C%20France%2C%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20and%20Spain%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20whom%20hold%20contracts%20that%20extend%20%26quot%3Bfar%20into%20the%20next%20decade.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Global%20Witness%20is%20calling%20for%20an%20EU%20ban%20on%20Russian%20LNG%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBuying%20Russian%20gas%20has%20the%20same%20impact%20as%20buying%20Russian%20oil.%20Both%20fund%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20every%20euro%20means%20more%20bloodshed%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jonathan%20Noronha-Gant%2C%20a%20senior%20fossil%20fuel%20campaigner%20at%20Global%20Witness.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20European%20countries%20decry%20the%20war%2C%20they're%20putting%20money%20into%20Putin's%20pockets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20EU%20is%20aware%20of%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20Kadri%20Simson%2C%20the%20EU's%20energy%20commissioner%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fenergy%2Flng-imports-test-eu-resolve-quit-russian-fossil-fuel-2023-04-12%2F%5C%22%3Ecalled%20on%20member%20states%20to%20stop%20buying%20Russian%20LNG%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20it's%20a%20%26quot%3Breputational%20risk.%26quot%3B%20Teresa%20Ribera%2C%20the%20Spanish%20energy%20minister%2C%20also%20called%20the%20situation%20%26quot%3Bquite%20absurd%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20same%20month%2C%20per%20the%20news%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20European%20Commission%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fenergy-european-union-record-volumes-russia-lng-gas-global-witness-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693469505000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6319b336adc999001884656e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fenergy-european-union-record-volumes-russia-lng-gas-global-witness-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20bloc%20is%20on%20track%20to%20import%20record%20volumes%20of%20Russian%20LNG%20this%20year%20to%20make%20up%20for%20lost%20piped%20gas.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22htan%40insider.com%20(Huileng%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fenergy-european-union-record-volumes-russia-lng-gas-global-witness-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIndia-Pakistan%20will%20always...%26quot%3B%3A%20Babar%20Azam%20ahead%20of%20high-octane%20clash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693469263000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103240149%2Cimgsize-89386.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fasia-cup%2Findia-pakistan-will-always-babar-azam-ahead-of-high-octane-ind-vs-pak-asia-cup-clash%2Farticleshow%2F103240021.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Brimming%20with%20confidence%20after%20their%20crushing%20win%20over%20minnows%20Nepal%20in%20their%20Asia%20Cup%202023%20opener%2C%20Pakistan%20captain%20Babar%20Azam%20said%20his%20team%20is%20100%20percent%20ready%20for%20much-awaited%20blockbuster%20against%20India.%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20will%20lock%20horns%20on%20September%202%20in%20Pallekele.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fasia-cup%2Findia-pakistan-will-always-babar-azam-ahead-of-high-octane-ind-vs-pak-asia-cup-clash%2Farticleshow%2F103240021.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Uttarakhand%20and%20the%20Futility%20of%20Trying%20to%20Determine%20'Carrying%20Capacities'%20of%20Towns%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31133235%2FUntitled-design-7-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20a%20recent%20newspaper%20report%2C%20the%20Uttarakhand%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20constitute%20a%20committee%20to%20determine%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccarrying%20capacity%E2%80%9D%20of%20various%20urban%20centres%20in%20the%20state.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20first%20sight%20this%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20worthwhile%20and%20much-needed%20exercise%2C%20as%20many%20mountain%20towns%20are%20faced%20with%20the%20problem%20of%20high%20population%20growth%20beyond%20the%20capacity%20of%20their%20civic%20administrations%20to%20cope%20with%20the%20consequences.%20There%20is%20also%20the%20fear%20that%20some%2C%20if%20not%20most%2C%20towns%20and%20cities%20may%20have%20already%20exceeded%20their%20carrying%20capacity.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20evidence%2C%20reports%20point%20to%20the%20perennial%20problems%20faced%20by%20them%20%E2%80%93%20water%20shortage%2C%20non-availability%20of%20land%20for%20housing%20and%20other%20needs%2C%20failure%20to%20deal%20with%20mounting%20waste%20management%2C%20traffic%20jams%20etc.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20throws%20up%20the%20troubling%20question%3A%20how%20do%20we%20deal%20with%20this%20development%3F%20Should%20we%2C%20or%20can%20we%2C%20remove%20some%20people%20from%20these%20places%3F%20Should%20we%2C%20or%20can%20we%2C%20prevent%20more%20people%20from%20coming%20in%20and%20settling%20in%20these%20places%3F%20Do%20we%20have%20any%20legal%20authority%20or%20instruments%20to%20justify%20such%20drastic%20action%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20useful%20to%20underline%20that%20while%20carrying%20capacity%20as%20a%20concept%20is%20being%20increasingly%20used%20to%20describe%20the%20situation%20in%20our%20towns%20and%20cities%2C%20and%20at%20a%20more%20general%20level%20to%20the%20planet%20earth%2C%20it%20is%20a%20difficult%20concept%20to%20operationalise%20and%20apply%20to%20human%20and%20social%20systems.%20Let%20us%20first%20try%20to%20understand%20what%20it%20implies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20To%20quote%20an%20oft-used%20definition%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%C2%A0carrying%20capacity%C2%A0of%20an%C2%A0environment%20is%20the%20maximum%20population%20size%20of%20a%20biological%C2%A0species%20that%20can%20be%20sustained%20by%20that%20specific%20environment%2C%20given%20the%20food%2C%20habitat%2C%20water%20and%20other%C2%A0resources%20available.%20The%20carrying%20capacity%20is%20defined%20as%20the%C2%A0environment%E2%80%99s%20maximal%20load%2C%20which%20in%C2%A0population%20ecology%C2%A0corresponds%20to%20the%20population%20equilibrium%2C%20when%20the%20number%20of%20deaths%20in%20a%20population%20equals%20the%20number%20of%20births%20(as%20well%20as%20immigration%20and%20emigration)%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20a%20cursory%20analysis%20of%20the%20concept%20highlights%20the%20problems%20in%20applying%20it%20to%20human%20and%20social%20systems.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fenvironment-ministry-and-uttarakhand-govt-flouted-rules-to-extend-river-mining%5C%22%3EDouble-Engine%20Govt%20in%20Uttarakhand%20Flouted%20Rules%20To%20Allow%20River%20Mining%3A%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20one%2C%20in%20human%20and%20social%20systems%20resources%20are%20not%20static%20and%20fixed%2C%20they%20are%20rather%20quite%20dynamic%20and%20flexible.%20For%20instance%2C%20shortfalls%20in%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Elocal%20food%20production%20can%20be%20overcome%20by%20imports%20from%20outside%20through%20channels%20of%20trade%20and%20commerce%20that%20have%20been%20created%20over%20millennia.%20In%20fact%20the%20process%20of%20urbanisation%20was%20facilitated%20by%20surplus%20food%20production%20in%20the%20countryside%20and%20its%20availability%20to%20urban%20areas%20through%20trading%20systems.%20Where%20it%20is%20not%20possibly%20to%20import%20a%20resource%20there%20technology%20provides%20the%20solution.%20For%20instance%2C%20shortage%20of%20water%20can%20be%20overcome%20by%20conveying%20it%20over%20short%20and%20long%20distances%20either%20by%20means%20of%20canals%20and%20pipelines%20using%20gravity%20flow%2C%20or%20where%20the%20terrain%20does%20not%20allow%20it%2C%20by%20use%20of%20pumps.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Similarly%2C%20shortage%20of%20land%20can%20by%20overcome%20by%20building%20multi-storey%20dwellings.%20Technology%20has%20also%20been%20used%20to%20augment%20resources%20and%20also%20create%20new%20resources.%20A%20good%20example%20is%20the%20seed-fertilizer%20package%2C%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98green%20revolution%E2%80%99%20that%20helped%20to%20augment%20food%20grain%20production%20manifold%20and%20prevent%20widespread%20food%20shortages%20in%20the%20decade%20of%20the%20seventies%20in%20the%20last%20century.%20Thus%20institutions%20(like%20the%20market)%20and%20technology%20have%20been%20instrumental%20in%20overcoming%20the%20constraints%20of%20carrying%20capacity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20notion%20of%20carrying%20capacity%20is%20best-suited%20for%20use%20in%20closed%20systems%20like%20animal%20preserves%20and%20national%20parks.%20Here%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20a%20predator%20species%20(carrying%20capacity)%20is%20based%20on%20the%20prey%20base%2C%20both%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20number%20and%20quality.%20Theoretically%2C%20carrying%20capacity%20depends%20on%20the%20availability%20of%20resources%20of%20various%20kinds%20%E2%80%93%20food%2C%20water%2C%20land%2C%20clean%20air%20etc%3B%20but%20it%20is%20ultimately%20determined%20by%20the%20resource%20that%20is%20in%20least%20supply.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fbadrinath-redevelopment-must-respect-its-heritage%5C%22%3ERedevelopment%20Projects%20at%20Badrinath%20Must%20Respect%20its%20Unique%20Natural%20and%20Spiritual%20Heritage%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20instance%20a%20closed%20system%20may%20have%20enough%20food%2C%20land%20and%20clean%20air%20available%2C%20but%20only%20limited%20supplies%20of%20water.%20Hence%20the%20carrying%20capacity%20of%20the%20place%20will%20be%20determined%20by%20the%20availability%20of%20water.%20Application%20of%20the%20concept%20to%20open%20systems%20is%20quite%20problematic%2C%20because%20as%20argued%20above%2C%20intervention%20of%20technology%20and%20socio-economic%20institutions%20like%20the%20market%20can%20modify%20it%20in%20significant%20ways.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EComing%20to%20the%20practical%20application%20of%20carrying%20capacity%20to%20social%20and%20human%20systems%2C%20I%20am%20aware%20of%20two%20attempts%20to%20do%20so%20in%20Uttarakhand.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20is%20a%20comprehensive%20study%20of%20carrying%20capacity%20of%20the%20Doon%20Valley%20spearheaded%20by%20the%20National%20Environmentalal%20Engineering%20Research%20Institute%20(NEERI)%20with%20involvement%20of%20a%20number%20of%20institutions.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20was%20submitted%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Environment%2C%20which%20sponsored%20the%20study%2C%20in%201996%20or%20thereabouts.%20The%20other%20is%20a%20study%20of%20the%20carrying%20capacity%20of%20Mussoorie%20undertaken%20by%20the%20LBS%20National%20Academy%20of%20Administration%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Monitoring%20Committee%20for%20the%20Doon%20Valley%20in%201997-98%20and%20published%20in%202001.%20Surprisingly%2C%20the%20Mussoorie%20study%20has%20no%20reference%20to%20the%20NEERI%20study%20despite%20the%20fact%20the%20latter%20has%20included%20data%20from%20Mussoorie%20in%20its%20report.%20The%20NEERI%20study%20has%20a%20wealth%20of%20quantified%20information%20on%20various%20environmental%20domains%20and%20issues%3B%20yet%20it%20refrains%20from%20putting%20a%20value%20or%20even%20a%20range%20of%20values%20to%20the%20carrying%20capacity%20of%20the%20Doon%20Valley.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20contents%20itself%20with%20identifying%20and%20analysing%20the%20various%20factors%20that%20have%20a%20bearing%20on%20the%20concept.%20The%20Mussoorie%20study%20is%20more%20explicit%20in%20quantifying%20carrying%20capacity.%20After%20analysing%20data%20on%20population%2C%20tourist%20arrivals%2C%20water%20availability%2C%20land%20area%20it%20concludes%20that%20based%20on%20water%20availability%20the%20carrying%20capacity%20of%20the%20town%20comes%20to%2046%2C666%20persons%20and%209%2C844%20overnight%20tourists%20in%201997.%20It%20estimated%20the%20population%20in%201997%20to%20be%2040%2C892%20rising%20to%2055%2C735%20or%2062%2C757%20in%202021%20(depending%20on%20assumed%20annual%20growth%20rate%20of%202%2C05%25%20or%202.6%25.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fjoshimath-himalayas-explainer-warnings-reports-construction-ntpc%5C%22%3EUncontrolled%20Construction%2C%20Ignored%20Warnings%3A%20How%20Joshimath%20Sank%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%20in%20terms%20of%20water%20availability%20the%20population%20of%20Mussoorie%20would%20not%20exceed%20the%20carrying%20capacity%20in%201997%2C%20but%20it%20would%20in%202021.%20However%20if%20tourist%20inflow%20into%20the%20town%20is%20taken%20into%20account%20then%20it%20would%20far%20exceed%20the%20carrying%20capacity%2C%20especially%20during%20the%20peak%20tourist%20season%20of%20April%20to%20July.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFaced%20with%20this%20situation%20the%20question%20that%20arises%20is%20how%20does%20one%20deal%20with%20the%20situation.%20This%20would%20be%20the%20situation%20in%20most%20of%20the%20towns%20of%20the%20state%20where%20the%20government%20proposes%20to%20undertake%20study%20of%20carrying%20capacity.%20This%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20most%20acute%20in%20towns%20falling%20on%20the%20Char%20Dham%20yatra%20route%20during%20the%20yatra%20season.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDepopulating%20these%20places%20or%20restricting%20the%20number%20of%20people%20undertaking%20Char%20Dham%20yatra%20is%20not%20an%20option%20the%20government%20would%20be%20willing%20to%20exercise.%20On%20the%20contrary%20the%20government%20has%20been%20encouraging%20more%20people%20to%20undertake%20the%20Char%20Dham%20yatra%20and%20providing%20facilities%20like%20wider%20roads%20and%20even%20ropeways%20to%20facilitate%20travel.%20In%20view%20of%20the%20above%20the%20sheer%20futility%20of%20the%20exercise%20is%20quite%20apparent.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EB.K.%20Joshi%20is%20the%20founder-director%20of%20Doon%20Library%20and%20Research%20Centre%2C%20Dehradun%20and%20is%20at%20present%20its%20adviser.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20first%20published%20in%20the%20Garhwal%20Post%2C%20Dehradun%2C%20on%20August%2027.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693469224000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31133235%2FUntitled-design-7-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Futtarakhand-carrying-capacities-hill-towns-char-dham%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20a%20difficult%20concept%20to%20operationalise%20and%20apply%20to%20human%20and%20social%20systems.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Futtarakhand-carrying-capacities-hill-towns-char-dham%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20the%20State%20Ceases%20to%20Act%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13152324%2FScreenshot-2023-07-13-at-3.22.09.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWest%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Nadia%20District%20in%20January%202019%2C%20declared%20the%20intention%20of%20her%20government%20to%20withdraw%20from%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20scheme%20%E2%80%93%20a%20centrally%20sponsored%20medical%20insurance%20program%20meant%20to%20cover%20hospital%20expenses%20of%20poor%20families%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20Rs%205%20lakhs%20a%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20her%20government%20entered%20into%20a%20memorandum%20of%20understanding%20(MoU)%20with%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20implement%20the%20scheme%20on%20a%20cost%20sharing%20basis%20where%2040%25%20of%20the%20expenses%20was%20to%20be%20borne%20by%20the%20state.%20The%20Union%20Government%20started%20sending%20the%20documents%20to%20the%20beneficiaries%20by%20Speed%20Post%20towards%20implementation%20of%20the%20scheme%20in%20different%20States.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBanerjee%E2%80%99s%20declaration%20on%20withdrawing%20from%20the%20programme%20came%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20that%20process.%20As%20soon%20as%20she%20announced%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20stand%2C%20miscreants%20in%20different%20districts%20started%20intimidating%20postal%20employees%20and%20physically%20resisted%20delivery%20of%20Ayushman%20letters%20already%20in%20transit.%20Media%20reports%20at%20the%20time%20revealed%20that%20when%20the%20issues%20were%20taken%20up%20by%20the%20post%20offices%20with%20local%20administration%2C%20no%20effective%20support%20was%20extended%20to%20the%20government%20body%20in%20carrying%20out%20its%20legal%20mandate%20%E2%80%93%20delivery%20of%20letters.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fayushman-bharat-cag-report-pmjay-corruption%5C%22%3ETreatment%20for%20the%20Dead%2C%20Discharge%20Before%20Surgery%20and%20the%20Many%20Problems%20of%20Ayushman%20Bharat%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBengal%20withdrew%20from%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20scheme%20in%20a%20dispute%20over%20branding.%20Why%20did%20the%20letters%20sent%20to%20the%20beneficiaries%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20have%20photos%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%20on%20it%20when%20the%20state%20was%20to%20bear%2040%25%20of%20the%20overall%20expenses%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20were%20also%20differences%20of%20opinion%20with%20the%20Union%20government%20on%20naming%20of%20the%20scheme.%20The%20issue%20here%20is%20not%20to%20judge%20the%20probity%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20withdraw%20from%20the%20scheme%20but%20to%20ask%20whether%20the%20state%20can%20remain%20a%20mute%20spectator%20when%20local%20miscreants%20physically%20resist%20the%20post%20office%2C%20a%20government%20department%2C%20in%20discharging%20its%20mandated%20role%20of%20delivering%20letters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20same%20lack%20of%20integrity%20was%20seen%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20state%20administration%20in%20the%20recently%20held%20three-tier%20Panchayat%20elections.%20About%2055%20lives%2C%20according%20to%20media%20reports%2C%20were%20lost%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbengal-panchayat-polls-tmc-position-violence%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eviolent%20political%20clashes%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Eafter%20the%20schedules%20were%20declared%20by%20the%20State%20Election%20Commission%20(SEC).%20This%20disgrace%20cannot%20be%20set%20off%20by%20the%20argument%20that%20in%20the%20past%20the%20state%20had%20witnessed%20a%20greater%20number%20of%20deaths%20in%20local%20body%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20logic%20that%20more%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20sympathisers%20died%20and%20hence%20opposition%20political%20parties%20were%20primarily%20responsible%20for%20violent%20clashes%20does%20not%20lead%20us%20anywhere.%20The%20administration%20responsible%20for%20conducting%20the%20election%20under%20the%20direction%20and%20supervision%20of%20the%20SEC%2C%20could%20not%20establish%20their%20intention%20to%20conduct%20a%20fair%20and%20fearless%20election.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Panchayat%20election%20of%20this%20year%2C%20particularly%20the%20way%20the%20ballots%20were%20counted%2C%20reminded%20us%20of%20the%20type%20of%20polls%20that%20we%20witnessed%20in%20some%20States%20of%20India%20in%20late-eighties%20and%20early-nineties%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftn-seshan-election-commissioner%5C%22%3Epre-Seshan%20days%3C%2Fa%3E.%20T.%20N.%20Seshan%20was%20a%20former%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20who%20strictly%20enforced%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20and%20led%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftn-seshan-election-commissioner%5C%22%3Ecritical%20electoral%20reforms%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%201990s.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftn-seshan-election-commissionerx%5C%22%3ET.%20N.%20Seshan%2C%20the%20Unyielding%20Force%20That%20Cleansed%20India%E2%80%99s%20Elections%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESEC%E2%80%99s%20silence%20made%20individual%20officers%20accountable%20for%20supervision%20of%20the%20counting%20process%2C%20solely%20responsible%20for%20any%20aberration.%20The%20way%20the%20commission%20communicated%20with%20the%20public%20through%20the%20press%2C%20their%20body%20language%2C%20their%20reluctance%20to%20engage%20central%20forces%2C%20their%20hurry%20to%20complete%20the%20election%20process%20by%20any%20means%2C%20never%20gave%20an%20impression%20that%20they%20were%20serious%20in%20conducting%20the%20election%20in%20a%20fair%20and%20fearless%20manner.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20any%20support%20from%20anywhere%20up%20in%20the%20hierarchy%2C%20if%20the%20Block%20level%20officers%20surrender%20to%20local%20pressure%20and%20counter-pressure%2C%20can%20we%20make%20them%20wholly%20responsible%20for%20their%20act%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhether%20the%20absence%20of%20large-scale%20aberrations%20could%20alter%20substantially%20the%20election%20results%20is%20not%20an%20important%20issue%20here.%20What%20is%20a%20new%20low%20is%20the%20way%20the%20election%20was%20held.%20After%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20government%20came%20to%20power%20in%202011%2C%20the%20first%20Panchayat%20election%20was%20held%20in%202013%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20the%20Saradha%20chit-fund%20controversy%2C%20under%20the%20stewardship%20of%20then%20state%20EC%2C%20Mira%20Pandey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20was%20the%20only%20time%20when%20local%20body%20elections%20were%20held%20in%20Bengal%20in%20five%20phases%20with%20the%20assistance%20of%20825%20companies%20of%20the%20Central%20Police%20Force.%20The%20commission%20had%20moved%20to%20the%20apex%20court%20on%20its%20own%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20led%20by%20the%20UPA%2C%20would%20arrange%20the%20requisite%20number%20of%20forces.%20The%20EC%20at%20the%20time%20was%20criticised%20for%20unusual%20activism.%20Though%20not%20to%20the%20same%20extent%2C%20many%20died%20in%20political%20clashes%20even%20in%202013.%20But%20nobody%20could%20allege%20that%20the%20EC%20was%20not%20serious%20in%20its%20intention%20to%20conduct%20a%20fair%20and%20fearless%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20EC%E2%80%99s%20effort%20gave%20credibility%20to%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20unprecedented%20victory%20in%20the%202013%20election.%20Unfortunately%2C%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20handsome%20victory%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%20this%20time%2C%20they%20will%20be%20denied%20that%20credibility.%20Those%20responsible%20for%20conducting%20the%20election%20must%20not%20forget%20the%20age-old%20proverb%20that%20%E2%80%9Cjustice%20must%20not%20only%20be%20done%2C%20but%20must%20also%20be%20seen%20to%20be%20done%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EGautam%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20former%20civil%20servant%20and%20an%20independent%20commentator%20on%20socio-economic%20issues%20and%20public%20policies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693468845000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13152324%2FScreenshot-2023-07-13-at-3.22.09.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhen-the-state-ceases-to-act%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20West%20Bengal%20Panchayat%20elections%20this%20year%20reminded%20us%20of%20the%20type%20of%20polls%20that%20we%20witnessed%20in%20some%20states%20in%20the%20late%201980s%20and%20early%201990s.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhen-the-state-ceases-to-act%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NRL%2C%20IIT-Guwahati%20sign%20pact%20to%20develop%20green%20carbon%20from%20bamboo%20dust%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693468303000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-09%2F07%2Ffull%2F1662524665-469.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fnrl-iit-guwahati-sign-pact-to-develop-green-carbon-from-bamboo-dust-123083100353_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20will%20be%20carried%20out%20as%20an%20industry-academia%20collaboration%2C%20and%20enhance%20the%20capacity%20of%20both%20NRL%20and%20IIT-G%20through%20provision%20of%20relevant%20data%20and%20information%20sharing%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fnrl-iit-guwahati-sign-pact-to-develop-green-carbon-from-bamboo-dust-123083100353_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fnrl-iit-guwahati-sign-pact-to-develop-gr