2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%227sflmq6o%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F7sflmq6o_g20-logo-650_625x300_31_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20nearly%207%20lakh%20plants%2C%20the%20forest%20department%20and%20the%20Delhi%20Parks%20and%20Garden%20Society%20have%20planted%203.75%20lakh%2C%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Municipal%20Council%20has%20planted%201%20lakh%20and%20the%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%20has%20placed%2050%2C000%20pots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E115-Foot%20Tricolour%20At%20Rajghat%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Public%20Works%20Derpartment%20(PWD)%20Minister%20Atishi%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20unique%20landscaping%20has%20been%20done%20at%20the%20Rajghat%20memorial%20complex%2C%20which%20is%20likely%20to%20see%20visits%20from%20several%20delegates%20during%20the%20G20%20Summit%2C%20and%20a%20115-foot%20Indian%20flag%20has%20also%20been%20installed%20at%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20that%20it%20was%20a%20matter%20of%20pride%20for%20both%20Delhi%20and%20the%20country%20that%20the%20summit%20is%20being%20held%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%20%26quot%3BPreparations%20for%20the%20G20%20Summit%20are%20in%20full%20swing%20across%20Delhi%2C%20with%20beautification%20efforts%20also%20underway.%20Today%2C%20I%20visited%20Rajghat%2C%20a%20location%20that%20many%20delegates%20and%20heads%20of%20countries%20will%20visit%20during%20the%20summit%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20PTI%20report%20quoted%20the%20minister%20as%20saying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22o8e8rocg%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fo8e8rocg_g20-rajghat-650_625x300_31_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20the%20past%20year%2C%20the%20stretch%20from%20Rajghat%20to%20Red%20Fort%20has%20undergone%20a%20stunning%20transformation%20led%20by%20the%20PWD.%20This%20area%20has%20been%20enhanced%20with%20features%20such%20as%20fountains%2C%20contemporary%20street%20art%2C%20open%20seating%20spaces%2C%20lighting%20and%20much%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20visiting%20Rajghat%2C%20the%20memorial%20to%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20is%20always%20a%20priority%20for%20any%20foreign%20delegation%20coming%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20such%2C%20the%20memorial%20has%20undergone%20unique%20landscaping.%20It%20has%20been%20adorned%20with%20greenery%20all%20around%2C%20a%20115-foot%20Indian%20flag%2C%20lighting%20installations%2C%20and%20much%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Atishi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20Monkey%20Business%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20monkey%20population%20burgeoning%20in%20several%20parts%20of%20Delhi%20-%20including%20the%20Lutyens'%20Delhi%20area%20-%20and%20several%20reports%20emerging%20of%20the%20animals%20attacking%20and%20biting%20people%2C%20authorities%20are%20taking%20steps%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20simians%20don't%20play%20spoilsport%20during%20the%20G20%20Summit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20important%20sites%2C%20including%20the%20main%20venue%20of%20the%20summit%20-%20Bharat%20Mandapam%20at%20Pragati%20Maidan%20-%20and%20hotels%20where%20foreign%20dignitaries%20and%20delegates%20will%20be%20staying%20are%20being%20covered%20to%20ensure%20the%20monkey%20hordes%20are%20not%20visible%20there%20during%20the%20event%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20government%20official%20told%20PTI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDMC%20vice-chairman%20Satish%20Upadhyay%20said%20the%20civic%20body%20will%20also%20deploy%2030-40%20trained%20persons%20who%20can%20mimic%20the%20sounds%20of%20langurs%20to%20scare%20away%20the%20monkeys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20trained%20persons%20are%20registered%20with%20us%20and%20they%20have%20been%20hired%20as%20they%20are%20effective%20in%20scaring%20away%20monkeys%20by%20mimicking%20sounds%20made%20by%20langurs.%20We%20will%20deploy%20one%20such%20person%20at%20each%20hotel%20where%20the%20delegates%20will%20be%20staying%2C%20as%20well%20as%20in%20places%20where%20monkey%20sightings%20are%20reported%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%20report%20said%20over%20a%20dozen%20langur%20cutouts%20have%20also%20been%20placed%20strategically%20in%20areas%2C%20including%20Sardar%20Patel%20Marg%2C%20that%20have%20a%20high%20monkey%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20official%20said%20monkeys%20have%20also%20damaged%20some%20plants%20and%20flowers%20that%20were%20part%20of%20the%20landscaping%20done%20for%20the%20G20%20Summit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESprucing%20Up%20Roads%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgencies%20have%20also%20been%20ensuring%20proper%20maintenance%20of%20the%2061%20roads%20that%20will%20be%20used%20by%20foreign%20dignitaries%20and%20delegates%20during%20the%20summit%2C%20and%20the%20work%20is%20being%20monitored%20by%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%2C%20Raj%20Niwas%20officials%20told%20PTI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22i31j7vbo%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fi31j7vbo_g20-sculpture-650_625x300_31_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%2015%2C000%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20solid%20waste%20have%20been%20cleared%20from%20such%20roads%20and%20locations%20by%20different%20agencies.%20Over%20100%20sculptures%20and%20150%20fountains%20with%20different%20designs%20have%20been%20installed%20at%20various%20locations%20to%20give%20Delhi%20an%20aesthetic%20look%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%20report%20said%20that%2C%20since%20July%2C%20Mr%20Saxena%20has%20held%20two%20dozen%20high-level%20meetings%20with%20officers%2C%20besides%20going%20on%20frequent%20visits%20to%20take%20stock%20of%20the%20preparations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELanguage%20No%20Bar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20went%20to%20several%20shops%20