Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F03131216%2FScreen-Shot-2021-11-03-at-1.07.58-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Vanthala%20Rasmo%2C%2050%2C%20a%20single%20woman%20from%20a%20%E2%80%98particularly%20vulnerable%20tribal%20group%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20Alluri%20Sitarama%20Raju%20district%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20consistent%20income%20from%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act%20(MGNREGA)%20is%20crucial%20for%20her%20sustenance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20especially%20important%20for%20Rasmo%20during%20summers%20when%20other%20livelihood%20options%20are%20scarce.%20Apart%20from%20the%20wages%20from%20MGNREGA%2C%20she%20relies%20on%20a%20meagre%20social%20security%20pension%20of%20Rs%203%2C000%20provided%20by%20the%20state%20government%20and%20cultivates%20turmeric%20on%20her%20one-acre%20forest%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20contemplates%20quitting%20MGNREGA%20work%20despite%20her%20financial%20constraints%2C%20due%20to%20the%20arduous%20wage%20collection%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20village%20is%20located%20deep%20in%20the%20Eastern%20Ghats%2C%20requiring%20her%20to%20trek%20three%20km%20to%20reach%20the%20nearest%20disbursement%20agency%2C%20and%20possibly%20an%20additional%20five%20km%20if%20a%20shared%20auto-rickshaw%20is%20unavailable.%20The%20journey%20involves%20climbing%20hillocks%2C%20traversing%20valleys%20and%20crossing%20crocodile-infested%20streams.%20She%20needs%20to%20put%20in%20all%20these%20efforts%20only%20to%20collect%20her%20MGNREGA%20payment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20struggle%20reflects%20a%20broader%20issue%20plaguing%20the%20cash%20collection%20process%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20tribal%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20struggles%20are%20often%20exacerbated%20by%20the%20scarcity%20of%20bank%20branches%20and%20the%20dearth%20of%20business%20correspondents%20or%20customer%20service%20points%20with%20limited%20internet%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusiness%20correspondents%20or%20customer%20service%20points%20are%20intermediaries%20designated%20by%20banks%20to%20provide%20basic%20services%20in%20areas%20where%20full-fledged%20bank%20branches%20are%20not%20feasible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMGNREGA%20workers%20who%20have%20completed%20their%20e-KYC%20at%20their%20bank%20branch%20can%20collect%20cash%20at%20these%20customer%20service%20points%20by%20presenting%20their%20Aadhaar%20card%20and%20biometrics.%20They%20can%20also%20approach%20b%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eusiness%20correspondents%20for%20the%20same%20purpose.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20people%20belonging%20to%20the%20Adivasi%20community%20face%20several%20challenges%2C%20such%20as%20disparities%20in%20the%20payment%20channels%20and%20their%20toilsome%20wage-collection%20journeys%2C%20in%20accessing%20MGNREGA%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Rasmo%E2%80%99s%20story%20shows%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20need%20for%20an%20accessible%20and%20accountable%20system%2C%20empowering%20labourers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmgnrega-workers-wages-nmms-app-aadhaar-based-payment-system%5C%22%3ELoopholes%20in%20the%20NMMS%20App%2C%20Aadhaar-Based%20Payment%20System%20Delaying%20MGNREGA%20Workers%E2%80%99%20Wages%3A%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20cost%20to%20access%20wages%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Paderu%20Integrated%20Tribal%20Development%20Agency%20(ITDA)%20area%2C%20the%20average%20number%20of%20people%20served%20by%20each%20bank%20branch%20stands%20at%2034%2C000%20for%20Adivasis%20and%207%2C000%20for%20non-Adivasis%2C%20per%20a%20study%20conducted%20by%20LibTech%20India%2C%20a%20research%20organisation%20in%20the%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20says%20that%20nearly%2085%25%20of%20the%20Adivasis%20in%20the%20Paderu%20ITDA%20receive%20their%20wages%20through%20business%20correspondents%20or%20customer%20service%20points%2C%20while%20only%2012.5%25%20have%20access%20to%20banks%2C%20and%20a%20mere%202.5%25%20use%20ATMs.%20This%20disparity%20is%20understandable%2C%20given%20the%20scarcity%20of%20bank%20branches%20in%20hilly%20regions.%20However%2C%20even%20when%20these%20are%20accessible%2C%20the%20MGNREGA%20workers%20are%20redirected%20to%20business%20correspondents%20or%20customer%20service%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERasmo%E2%80%99s%20case%20shows%20how%20Adivasis%20face%20significant%20challenges%20as%20they%20need%20to%20travel%20long%20distances%20to%20reach%20the%20disbursement%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELibTech%E2%80%99s%20study%20shows%20that%20approximately%2037%25%20of%20the%20workers%20have%20to%20commute%20more%20than%2010%20kilometers%20to%20access%20their%20wages%2C%20with%20even%20higher%20percentages%20observed%20for%20bank%20branches%20(48%25)%20and%20ATMs%20(58%25).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraversing%20such%20distances%20incurs%20transport%20and%20food%20expenses%2C%20with%2050%25%20of%20workers%20spending%20over%20Rs%20200%20and%2010%25%20of%20them%20spending%20over%20Rs%20400%20during%20a%20single%20visit.%20This%20leads%20to%20many%20compromising%20their%20MGNREGA%20wages%20for%20the%20corresponding%20number%20of%20days%20spent%20collecting%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERasmo%E2%80%99s%20situation%20is%20not%20unique.%20As%20per%20the%20study%2C%20about%2075%25%20of%20the%20workers%20miss%20work%20due%20to%20their%20visits%20to%20the%20disbursement%20agency.%20Over%2090%25%20of%20them%20miss%20at%20least%20one%20day%20of%20work%20and%2025%25%20miss%20at%20least%20two%20days%20of%20work.%20As%20a%20result%2C%2095%25%20of%20those%20who%20miss%20work%20sacrifice%20more%20than%20Rs%20100%2C%20and%2075%25%20of%20them%20forego%20Rs%20200%20or%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Falmost-twenty-percent-active-nrega-workers-ineligible-abps%5C%22%3EClose%20to%2020%25%20Of%20Active%20MGNREGS%20Workers%20Ineligible%20for%20Soon-To-Be%20Compulsory%20Aadhaar-Based%20Pay%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20lack%20of%20reliable%20information%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20reliable%20information%20on%20wage%20credit%2C%20Rasmo%20also%20faces%20difficulty%20in%20determining%20when%20to%20collect%20her%20wages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20one-third%20of%20the%20workers%20make%20multiple%20visits%20to%20the%20disbursement%20agencies%20due%20to%20this%20issue.%20Less%20than%20half%20of%20them%20receive%20updates%20through%20official%20channels%20or%20SMS%20notifications%2C%20leading%20to%20conflicting%20information%20and%20confusion.%20These%20challenges%20are%20coupled%20with%20other%20issues%20such%20as%20overcrowding%2C%20network%20failures%2C%20and%20cash%20shortages%20at%20disbursement%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver-reliance%20on%20business%20correspondents%20and%20customer%20service%20points%20creates%20additional%20hurdles%20for%20these%20workers%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20accessing%20their%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20fraudulent%20cases%20have%20also%20occurred%2C%20raising%20serious%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20case%20is%20of%20Gollori%20Juruko%2C%20an%20unlettered%20Adivasi%20NREGA%20worker%2C%20who%20discovered%20missing%20wages%20from%20his%20bank%20account%20due%20to%20alleged%20fraudulent%20actions%20by%20the%20local%20customer%20service%20point.%20The%20worker%20reported%20the%20issue%20to%20the%20local%20officials%3B%20however%2C%20they%20were%20unsure%20of%20the%20appropriate%20action%2C%20and%20only%20suggested%20him%20to%20file%20a%20police%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20recommends%20expanding%20bank%20branches%2C%20ATMs%2C%20and%20moving%20business%20correspondents%20and%20customer%20service%20points%20closer%20to%20MGNREGA%20workers.%20A%20strong%20infrastructure%2C%20including%20electricity%2C%20internet%20connectivity%2C%20and%20offline%20capabilities%2C%20is%20also%20vital%20for%20smoother%20wage%20disbursement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20social%20audits%20should%20observe%20the%20performance%20of%20business%20correspondents%20and%20customer%20service%20points%2C%20and%20customers%20should%20receive%20a%20copy%20of%20their%20rights%20in%20their%20local%20language.%20The%20state%20must%20share%20comprehensive%20information%20with%20the%20community%20regarding%20the%20work-payment%20cycle%20in%20MGNREGA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20successful%20door-to-door%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Farticle%2Fandhra-govt-continues-door-delivery-pensions-59-lakh-beneficiaries-covered-119263%5C%22%3Edelivery%20of%20social%20security%20pensions%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20shows%20that%20efficient%20cash%20delivery%20is%20possible.%20Workers%20must%20have%20the%20choice%20to%20decide%20how%20and%20where%20they%20can%20access%20their%20wages%2C%20empowering%20them%20to%20align%20their%20decisions%20with%20their%20needs%2C%20enhancing%20convenience%20and%20accessibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20solutions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenges%20highlighted%20in%20the%20report%20regarding%20wage%20payments%20under%20MGNREGA%20in%20Paderu%20ITDA%20likely%20extend%20to%20other%20tribal%20areas%20and%20cash%20transfer%20programmes%20due%20to%20consistent%20engagement%20between%20Adivasis%20and%20disbursement%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnsuring%20funds%20reach%20the%20people%20promptly%20is%20crucial.%20The%20concerned%20ministries%20should%20involve%20local%20elected%20bodies%20to%20oversee%20fund%20transfers%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20scheduled%20areas%20where%20the%20Panchayat%20(Extension%20to%20Scheduled%20Areas)%20Act%2C%201996%20mandates%20the%20involvement%20of%20gram%20sabhas%20in%20decision-making.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stories%20of%20Rasmo%20and%20Juruko%20serve%20as%20poignant%20reminders%20of%20the%20hardships%20Adivasis%20endure%20in%20accessing%20MGNREGA%20wages%20and%20banking%20services.%20To%20alleviate%20these%20hardships%2C%20we%20must%20address%20disparities%20in%20payment%20channels%2C%20reduce%20travel%20burden%2C%20strengthen%20the%20monitoring%20of%20business%20correspondents%20and%20customer%20service%20points%2C%20and%20enhance%20information%20dissemination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlacing%20local%20communities%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20decision-making%20can%20help%20in%20an%20inclusive%20and%20empowering%20system%2C%20eradicating%20unnecessary%20hardships%20and%20supporting%20their%20rightful%20quest%20for%20a%20better%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EE.A.S.%20Sarma%20is%20a%20former%20secretary%20at%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20and%20Chakradhar%20Buddha%20is%20affiliated%20with%20LibTech%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693467033000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F03131216%2FScreen-Shot-2021-11-03-at-1.07.58-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Funderstanding-the-issues-plaguing-mgnrega-wage-collection-process-in-andhra-pradeshs-tribal-areas%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Adivasi%20community%20faces%20several%20challenges%2C%20such%20as%20disparities%20in%20the%20payment%20channels%20and%20their%20toilsome%20wage-collection%20journeys%2C%20in%20accessing%20MGNREGA%20wages.%20Such%20struggles%20are%20often%20exacerbated%20by%20the%20scarcity%20of%20bank%20branches%20in%20the%20areas.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Funderstanding-the-issues-plaguing-mgnrega-wage-collection-process-in-andhra-pradeshs-tribal-areas%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20right%20bedroom%20temperature%20that%20can%20help%20prevent%20diseases%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693467000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F