%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftalks-between-union-government-and-ladakh-bodies-set-to-resume%5C%22%3Eresumed%20talks%20with%20the%20leadership%20of%20Ladakh%20in%20June%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%202023%20after%20the%20latter%20had%20refused%20to%20speak%20with%20a%20high-powered%20committee%20constituted%20under%20the%20chairmanship%20of%20Union%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20home%20Nitayanand%20Rai%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693465209000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F13114439%2FLadakh2.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwe-were-previously-benefiting-from-representation-special-status-and-statehood-leh-kargil-group%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIf%20the%20government%20fails%20to%20provide%20good%20governance%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh%2C%20then%20why%20was%20the%20decision%20made%20to%20separate%20us%20from%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%3F%E2%80%9D%20KDA%E2%80%99s%20Sajjad%20Kargili%20asked.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwe-were-previously-benefiting-from-representation-special-status-and-statehood-leh-kargil-group%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Doctor%20Who%20Studied%20Near-Death%20Experiences%20Says%20This%20About%20Afterlife%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENeedless%20to%20say%2C%20death%20is%20the%20most%20profound%20and%20mysterious%20aspect%20of%20life%20for%20most%20humans.%20Many%20of%20us%20also%20keep%20wondering%20what%20happens%20after%20death%2C%20but%20there%20are%20no%20answers%20to%20this%20mind-bending%20question.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20radiation%20oncologist%20in%20the%20US%20who%20claims%20to%20have%20studied%20more%20than%205%2C000%20near-death%20experiences%20(NDE)%20believes%20that%20life%20exists%20after%20death%2C%20''without%20a%20doubt.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Dr.%20Jeffrey%20Long's%20fascination%20with%20near-death%20experiences%20also%20led%20to%20him%20founding%20the%C2%A0Near-Death%20Experience%20Research%20Foundation%20in%201998.%20Recently%2C%20he%20published%20an%20essay%20based%20on%20his%20experiences%20in%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fnear-death-experiences-research-doctor-life-after-death-afterlife-2023-8%5C%22%3EInsider%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fem%3EHe%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Edefined%20NDEs%20as%20''someone%20who%20is%20either%20comatose%20or%20clinically%20dead%2C%20without%20a%20heartbeat%2C%20having%20a%20lucid%20experience%20where%20they%20see%2C%20hear%2C%20feel%20emotions%2C%20and%20interact%20with%20other%20beings.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20he%20has%20been%C2%A0collecting%20stories%20from%20those%20who%20have%20reported%20NDEs%20and%20has%20been%20scientifically%20analysing%20the%20accounts.%20While%20each%20story%20is%20different%2C%20of%20course%2C%20he%20noticed%20a%20similar%C2%A0pattern%20of%20events%20emerging%20in%20a%20predictable%20order%20in%20many%20cases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20him%2C%20about%2045%25%20of%20people%20who%20have%20an%20NDE%20report%20an%20out-of-body%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Long%20explained%20that%20people%20claim%20'their%20consciousness%20separates%20from%20their%20physical%20body%2C%20usually%20hovering%20above%2C''%20allowing%20them%20to%20see%20and%20hear%20what%20happens%20around%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''After%20the%20out-of-body%20experience%2C%20people%20say%20they're%20transported%20into%20another%20realm.%20Many%20pass%20through%20a%20tunnel%20and%20experience%20a%20bright%20light.%20Then%2C%20they're%20greeted%20by%20deceased%20loved%20ones%2C%20including%20pets%2C%20who%20are%20in%20the%20prime%20of%20their%20lives.%20Most%20people%20report%20an%20overwhelming%20sense%20of%20love%20and%20peace.%20They%20feel%20like%20this%20other%20realm%20is%20their%20real%20home%2C''%20Mr%20Long%20further%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20added%20witnesses'%20statements%20to%20support%20the%20narratives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20an%20example%2C%20he%20said%2C%20''One%20woman%20lost%20consciousness%20while%20riding%20her%20horse%20on%20a%20trail.%20Her%20body%20stayed%20on%20the%20trail%20while%20her%20consciousness%20traveled%20with%20her%20horse%20as%20he%20galloped%20back%20to%20the%20barn.%20Later%2C%20she%20was%20able%20to%20describe%20exactly%20what%20happened%20at%20the%20barn%20because%20she%20had%20seen%20it%20despite%20her%20body%20not%20being%20there.%20Others%20who%20hadn't%20spoken%20to%20her%20confirmed%20her%20account.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20admitted%20that%20he%20never%20found%20any%20''scientific%20explanation%20for%20these%20experiences.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''I've%20read%20brain%20research%20and%20considered%20every%20possible%20explanation%20for%20NDEs.%20The%20bottom%20line%20is%20that%20none%20of%20them%20hold%20water%2C''%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20doctors%20who%20have%20been%20conducting%20similar%20research%20also%20agreed%20with%20Dr.%20Long%20and%20cited%20a%20few%20familiar%20traits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693465200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fen3ujp2_life-after-death_625x300_31_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-doctor-who-studied-5-000-near-death-experiences-says-this-about-afterlife-4344412%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20doctor%20in%20the%20US%20who%20claims%20to%20have%20studied%20more%20than%205%2C000%20near-death%20experiences%20(NDE)%20believes%20that%20life%20exists%20after%20death%2C%20''without%20a%20doubt.''%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-doctor-who-studied-5-000-near-death-