2%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20today%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20elections%20could%20be%20conducted%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20anytime%20now%2C%20but%20the%20decision%20lies%20with%20the%20Election%20Commission%20and%20the%20state%20poll%20panel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20five-judge%20bench%20headed%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20was%20told%20by%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20that%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20will%20be%20held%20in%20three%20stages%20-%20first%20there%20will%20be%20panchayat%20polls%2C%20second%20municipal%20polls%20and%20then%20legislative%20assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statements%20came%20during%20the%20hearing%20of%20a%20bunch%20of%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20scrapping%20of%20Article%20370.%20The%20Centre%20had%20earlier%20argued%20that%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20was%20one%20of%20a%20kind%20and%20the%20bifurcation%20was%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20last%20hearing%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20laid%20emphasis%20on%20the%20need%20to%20restore%20democracy%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20which%20has%20been%20without%20an%20elected%20government%20since%20June%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20today's%20hearing%2C%20the%20Centre%20though%20refused%20to%20provide%20a%20timeframe%20on%20restoration%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20statehood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20arguments%2C%20is%20if%20due%20process%20was%20followed%20while%20abrogating%20Article%20370%20and%20dividing%20state%20into%20two%20union%20territories-%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeaders%20and%20petitioners%20from%20Ladakh%20have%20expressed%20their%20disappointment%20over%20The%20Solicitor%20General's%20statement%20that%20Ladakh%20will%20remain%20a%20Union%20Territory.%20Over%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20there%20have%20been%20massive%20protests%20in%20Ladakh%20demanding%20statehood%20for%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20scrapping%20Article%2037