nance%20tools%2C%20which%20are%20said%20to%20be%20democratising%20service%20delivery%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Tribune%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fmother-of-democracy-exhibition-to-greet-leaders-at-delhi-summit-venue-539804%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20principal%20secretary%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20P.K.%20Mishra%2C%20held%20the%20ninth%20review%20meeting%20of%20the%20G20%20Coordination%20Committee%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20August%2030.%20He%20took%20stock%20of%20arrangements%20for%20the%20G20%20New%20Delhi%20Leaders%E2%80%99%20Summit%2C%20including%20logistical%2C%20protocol%2C%20security%2C%20and%20media-related%20arrangements.%20The%20meeting%20was%20attended%20by%20senior%20officers%20from%20the%20G20%20secretariat%20and%20ministries%20of%20external%20affairs%2C%20home%2C%20culture%2C%20information%20and%20broadcasting%2C%20and%20telecom%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1953513%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20a%20release%20from%20Press%20Information%20Bureau%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EItems%20from%20installations%20to%20give%20a%20facelift%20to%20Delhi%20ahead%20of%20summit%20stolen%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%E2%80%99s%20attempts%20to%20give%20a%20facelift%20to%20the%20national%20capital%20ahead%20of%20the%20summit%20are%20running%20into%20trouble%20with%20many%20items%20used%20in%20various%20installations%20in%20and%20around%20the%20city%20being%20stolen.%20High-end%20lights%2C%20copper%20wires%2C%20and%20even%20cheap%20minor%20fittings%20like%20nozzles%20have%20been%20stolen%20from%20these%20installations%2C%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fdelhi-news%2Fthieves-target-new-delhi-installations-ahead-of-g20-summit-stealing-lights-copper-wires-and-rubber-nozzles-officials-101693416731450.html%5C%22%3E