0Search%20results%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.google%2Fintl%2Fen-in%2Fproducts%2Fexplore-communicate%2Fbringing-search-labs-and-generative-ai-experiences-to-india%2F%5C%22%3EGoogle%20blog%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20generative%20AI%20will%20help%20users%20better%20understand%20topics%20faster%2C%20uncover%20new%20viewpoints%20and%20insights%20and%20get%20things%20done%20more%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20short%20videos%20and%20images%20on%20the%20Search%20result%20page%20will%20be%20based%20on%20a%20conversational%20pattern%2C%20covering%20some%20of%20the%20aspects%20of%20the%20topic%20to%20give%20users%20the%20complete%20picture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EExplaining%20it%20further%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20an%20example%2C%20Google%20said%20if%20a%20user%20asks%20a%20question%20like%20%26quot%3BWhich%20is%20a%20good%20beginner%20trek%20in%20Himachal%20and%20how%20to%20prepare%20for%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20generative%20AI%20will%20help%20him%2Fher%20to%20break%20down%20the%20topic%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AI-powered%20Search%20will%20give%20an%20overview%20of%20key%20information%20to%20consider%2C%20with%20links%20to%20dig%20deeper%20-%20such%20as%20covering%20a%20follow-up%20question%20%26quot%3BHow%20to%20take%20great%20photos%20on%20a%20trek%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContext%20will%20be%20carried%20over%20from%20question-to-question.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESwitching%20between%20languages%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoogle%20Search%20will%20also%20allow%20users%20to%20switch%20from%20an%20English%20result%20to%20Hindi%20by%20tapping%20the%20language%20toggle%20button.%20It%20will%20also%20read%20out%20the%20results%20with%20the%20help%20of%20text-to-speech%20feature%20(present%20as%20Listen%20button).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoogle%20said%20it%20will%20soon%20add%20a%20microphone%20icon%20in%20conversational%20mode%20to%20allow%20users%20to%20ask%20follow-up%20questions%20instead%20of%20typing%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20features%20in%20AI-based%20Search%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Google%20blog%20said%20that%20it%20will%20use%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20voices%20for%20the%20Search%20results.%20It%20added%20that%20Search%20ads%20will%20continue%20to%20appear%20in%20dedicated%20ad%20slots%20throughout%20the%20page.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20feature%20was%20so%20far%20available%20only%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20After%20its%20rollout%20in%20India%20and%20Japan%2C%20Google%20said%20users%20will%20have%20the%20choice%20to%20opt%20in%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693460700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2015-06%2Fgoogle-search_650x400_41434102012.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgoogle-adds-new-features-to-ai-based-search-in-india-all-you-need-to-know-4344321%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Google%20is%20expanding%20AI's%20footprint%20in%20its%20Search%20results.%20The%20latest%20rollout%20in%20India%20and%20Japan%20adds%20key%20new%20features.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgoogle-adds-new-features-to-ai-based-search-in-india-all-you-need-to-know-4344321%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgoogle-adds-new-features-to-ai-based-search-in-india-all-you-need-to-know-4344321%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgoogle-adds-new-features-to-ai-based-search-in-india-all-you-need-to-know-4344321%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22At%20least%2047%20people%20have%20died%20in%20fire%20in%20building%20in%20South%20Africa's%20biggest%20city%2C%20authorities%20say%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693460483000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103234635%2Cimgsize-11898