0that%2C%20who%20is%20finding%20this%20so%20hard%20to%20digest%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20tried%20to%20take%20my%20stand%20to%20the%20vice-chancellor.%20I%20am%20able%20to%20say%20these%20things%20in%20front%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20the%20education%20minister%2C%20in%20parliament%2C%20on%20the%20streets%2C%20in%20newspapers%20%E2%80%93%20but%20I%20cannot%20say%20them%20in%20my%20own%20university%20to%20other%20teachers.%20What%20is%20this%20fear%3F%20Is%20this%20how%20India%20will%20become%20a%20%E2%80%98vishwaguru%E2%80%99%3F%20By%20locking%20up%20our%20universities%3F%20After%20today%2C%20I%20will%20even%20write%20a%20plain%20letter%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20education%20minister%2C%20and%20point%20out%20what%20is%20going%20on%20under%20their%20noses.%20If%20they%20do%20not%20agree%20with%20such%20actions%2C%20they%20must%20put%20an%20end%20to%20them%20immediately.%20Because%20we%20cannot%20just%20watch%20a%20university%20die%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20concluded%20in%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Democratic%20United%20Teachers%E2%80%99%20Alliance%20(DUTA)%20%E2%80%93%20a%20group%20of%20DU%20teachers%20%E2%80%93%20has%20also%20come%20out%20strongly%20against%20the%20cancellation.%20This%20%E2%80%9Cis%20one%20more%20instance%20of%20institutionalisation%20of%20an%20intolerant%20and%20bigoted%20culture%20in%20the%20University%20of%20Delhi%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20statement%20signed%20by%20DUTA%20Coordination%20Committee%20convenor%20Nandita%20Narain%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTypically%2C%20such%20exclusion%20is%20carried%20out%20by%20leaving%20out%20persons%20with%20contrarian%20views.%20It%20appears%20that%20Prof.%20Manoj%20Jha%20got%20invited%20due%20to%20oversight%20by%20the%20vigilante%20since%20he%20is%20known%20for%20his%20criticism%20of%20the%20ideological%20position%20of%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20both%20as%20an%20academic%20and%20political%20social%20worker.%20It%20is%20a%20disgrace%20fo