%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnnamed%20officials%20told%20the%20paper%20that%20two%20battalions%20of%20the%20India%20Reserve%20Battalion%2C%20a%20special%20armed%20force%20of%20the%20state%2C%20were%20deployed%20in%20the%20area.%20The%20two%20jawans%20from%20among%20them%20who%20received%20injuries%20are%20recovering%2C%20as%20are%20the%20five%20civilians%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20firing%20between%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20militants%20is%20learned%20to%20have%20stopped%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECBI%20takes%20over%2027%20FIRs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20agency%20PTI%20has%20reported%20that%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20has%20taken%20over%20cases%20pertaining%20to%2027%20FIRs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20has%20thus%20registered%2027%20corresponding%20cases%2C%20out%20of%20which%2019%20are%20of%20crime%20against%20women%2C%20three%20pertain%20to%20an%20armory%20loot%20by%20a%20mob%2C%20two%20are%20of%20murder%20and%20one%20each%20of%20rioting%20and%20murder%2C%20kidnapping%20and%20general%20criminal%20conspiracy%2C%20the%20agency%20report%20said%2C%20quoting%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20CBI%20team%20of%2053%20officers%2C%20of%20whom%2029%20are%20women%2C%20are%20looking%20into%20the%20Manipur%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20who%20spoke%20to%20PTI%20said%20the%20investigators%20were%20keen%20to%20avoid%20allegations%20of%20bias%20while%20looking%20into%20the%20ethnic%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20said%20several%20of%20these%20cases%20being%20probed%20by%20the%20CBI%20may%20attract%20provisions%20of%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%2C%201989%2C%20which%20can%20be%20probed%20by%20an%20officer%20of%20the%20rank%20of%20deputy%20superintendent%20of%20police%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20agency%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMeira%20Paibis%20versus%20Assam%20Rifles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20fissures%20between%20the%20Meitei%20women%20activists%20called%20Meira%20Paibis%20and%20the%20paramilitary%20force%20Assam%20Rifles%20grows%2C%20with%20the%20former%20reviving%20the%20demand%20for%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20removal%20from%20strife-torn%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fnorth-east%2Fmeitei-women-revive-demand-for-removal-of-assam-rifles-from-strife-torn-manipur%2Fcid%2F1962709%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20representatives%20of%20the%20Committee%20on%20Mass%20Protest%20Against%20Assam%20Rifles%20called%20on%20governor%20Anusuiya%20Uikey%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20August%2030.%20The%20group%20reminded%20the%20government%20of%20their%20August%209%20memorandum%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20through%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20those%20in%20the%20delegation%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20they%20asked%20the%20governor%20what%20the%20status%20of%20their%20memorandum%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20said%20she%20had%20discussed%20the%20issue%20with%20the%20Centre%20and%20would%20discuss%20it%20again.%20We%20want%20their%20removal%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Meira%20Paibi%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECPI(M)%20delegation%20finds%20state%20deeply%20divided%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20CPI(M)%20central%20committee%20delegation%20of%20party%20general%20secretary%20Sitaram%20Yechury%2C%20along%20with%20Jitendera%20Choudhury%2C%20Debolina%20Hembram%20and%20Suprakash%20Talukdar%2C%20that%20visited%20the%20state%20from%20August%2018-20%2C%20found%20the%20stage%20deeply%20divided%20along%20ethnic%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20segregation%20is%20stark%3A%20the%20Imphal%20Valley%20no%20longer%20houses%20anyone%20from%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community%2C%20even%20government%20officials%20who%E2%80%99ve%20moved%20to%20Kuki-Zo%20areas%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20on%20the%20party%20paper%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20delegation%20visited%20the%20Saithong%20Relief%20camp%20in%20Moirang%2C%20where%20370%20Meitei%20individuals%20sought%20refuge%20since%20May%204.%20After%20the%20inauguration%20of%20a%20relief%20distribution%20effort%2C%20the%20delegation%20proceeded%20to%20Churachandpur%20district%20and%20visited%20two%20relief%20camps%20at%20Koite%20with%20200%20Kuki-Zo%20residents%20and%20another%20at%20Saidan.%20This%20camp%2C%20the%20report%20says%2C%20accommodated%20Hmar%20and%20Thadao%20speakers%20who%20fled%20Sangang%20and%20Lanja%20villages%20on%20May%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20delegation%20also%20met%20religious%20heads%20like%20Archbishop%20Dominic%20Luman%2C%20law%20enforcement%20officials%20like%20Churachandpur%E2%80%99s%20DC%20and%20SP%2C%20and%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Governor%2C%20Anusuiya%20Uikey%2C%20and%20with%C2%A0Churachandpur%E2%80%99s%20civil%20society%20groups%20and%20prominent%20individuals%20at%20the%20Kuki%20INPT%20office%20in%20Tuibong.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693456841000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31100847%2FF4tkKVqaYAAQQFq.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-violence-firing-cbi-meira-paibis-cpim-delegation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20firing%20between%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20militants%20near%20Naransena%20is%20learned%20to%20have%20stopped%20now.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-violence-firing-cbi-meira-paibis-cpim-delegation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Virginia%20woman%20arrested%20for%20sexually%20abusing%2015-year-old%20twins%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693455823000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103231261%2Cimgsize-1014214.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%