uto-pay%20and%20subscriptions%2C%20it's%20easier%20than%20ever%20to%20access%20goods%20and%20services%20from%20around%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20and%20easier%20than%20ever%20to%20forget%20exactly%20which%20services%20you're%20continually%20paying%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20economist%20Neale%20Mahoney%20realized%20he%20forgot%20to%20cancel%20his%20Peacock%20subscription%20and%20paid%20for%20several%20months%20longer%20than%20he%20intended%2C%20he%20got%20curious%20about%20how%20many%20people%20were%20having%20the%20same%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2023%2F08%2F30%2F1196059950%2Fstreaming-monthly-subscriptions-cancel-peacock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMahoney%20told%20NPR%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20and%20another%20colleague%20from%20Stanford%20University%20joined%20forces%20with%20an%20economist%20at%20Texas%20A%26amp%3BM%20University%20to%20comb%20through%20millions%20of%20credit%20card%20records%20in%20a%20natural%20experiment%20%E2%80%94%20an%20observational%20study%20on%20when%20people%20canceled%20their%20subscriptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20realized%20that%20when%20your%20credit%20card%20expires%20or%20you%20lose%20your%20credit%20card%20and%20get%20a%20new%20one%20in%20the%20mail%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20get%20an%20email%20from%20all%20the%20companies%20where%20you%20have%20a%20subscription%20that%20says%2C%20'Can%20you%20log%20in%20again%20and%20update%20your%20payment%20information%3F'%26quot%3B%20Mahoney%20said%20to%20NPR.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20that%20happened%2C%20according%20to%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnmahoney.people.stanford.edu%2Fsites%2Fg%2Ffiles%2Fsbiybj23976%2Ffiles%2Fmedia%2Ffile%2Fsubscriptions.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresulting%20paper%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20consumers%20had%20to%20re-subscribe%20with%20a%20different%20card%2C%20there%20was%20a%20sharp%20drop%20in%20subscription%20renewal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoughly%208%25%20of%20customers%20cancel