itle%22%3A%22At%20INDIA's%20Mumbai%20Meet%2C%20Seat-Sharing%20to%20Take%20Back%20Seat%20as%20Focus%20Is%20On%20Common%20Programme%2C%20Vision%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F18155503%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-18-at-1.20.10-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20As%20the%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%20parties%20are%20all%20set%20for%20their%20third%20meeting%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20two%20developments%20preceding%20it%20may%20have%20just%20foregrounded%20the%20ideological%20contours%20of%20the%20grand%20coalition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20day%20ahead%20of%20the%20meeting%2C%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20and%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20stakeholders%20of%20INDIA%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%20declared%20that%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20census%20has%20been%20completed%20and%20its%20report%20will%20be%20out%20soon.%20Down%20south%2C%20the%20Congress%20government%20in%20Karnataka%20kickstarted%20the%20Gruha%20Lakshmi%20scheme%20that%20guarantees%20a%20sum%20of%20Rs%202000%20per%20month%20to%20women%20head%20of%20families%2C%20in%20what%20is%20the%20biggest%20direct%20benefit%20transfer%20scheme%20in%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20demand%20for%20a%20pan-India%20caste%20census%20has%20slowly%20been%20gaining%20ground%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20Mandal%20parties%2C%20which%20believe%20that%20having%20a%20caste%20census%20may%20allow%20governments%20to%20pass%20on%20welfare%20benefits%20in%20a%20better%20and%20more%20organised%20way.%20The%20BJP%20has%20been%20mostly%20reluctant%2C%20or%20even%20confused%2C%20in%20getting%20a%20caste%20census%20implemented%2C%20as%20could%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20flip-flop%20over%20the%20issue%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20However%2C%20Mandal%20parties%20like%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%2C%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%2C%20and%20even%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20have%20been%20consistent%20in%20their%20demand%20to%20get%20it%20implemented.%20With%20Bihar%20showing%20the%20way%2C%20it%20is%20most%20likely%20that%20the%20caste%20census%20will%20dominate%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%E2%80%99s%20talk%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20with%20the%20alliance%20hoping%20that%20the%20issue%20could%20reorient%20political%20debates%20and%20discussions%20away%20from%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20brand%20of%20nationalism%20and%20the%20Brand%20Modi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20implemented%20the%20Gruha%20Lakshmi%20scheme%20on%20the%20100th%20day%20of%20the%20Siddaramaiah-led%20Karnataka%20government.%20Speaking%20at%20the%20inauguration%20at%20Mysuru%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20five%20poll%20guarantees%2C%20four%20of%20which%20have%20already%20been%20implemented%2C%20were%20not%20merely%20schemes%20but%20%E2%80%9Ca%20governance%20model%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20one%20that%20is%20geared%20towards%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20marginalised%20sections%20and%20the%20poor.%20Many%20Congress%20leaders%20also%20spoke%20about%20how%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20schemes%20in%20Karnataka%20were%20actually%20a%20payback%20to%20the%20taxpayers%20of%20the%20country%2C%20contrasting%20that%20with%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20favouritism%20towards%20%E2%80%9Cbillionaires%E2%80%9D.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Gandhi%20emphasised%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20responsiveness%20to%20people%E2%80%99s%20problems%20and%20struggles%2C%20even%20as%20he%20insisted%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20is%20committed%20to%20the%20empowerment%20of%20women.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20combination%20of%20universal%20welfarist%20measures%20and%20social%20justice%20politics%20does%20not%20merely%20reflect%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%E2%80%99s%20political%20posturing%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20polls%20but%20also%20swiftly%20fuses%20the%20different%20ideological%20roots%20of%20the%2026%20parties%20under%20one%20common%20umbrella.%20The%20coming%20together%20of%20these%20historically%20inimical%20parties%20can%20be%20credited%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20aggression%20against%20the%20opposition.%20If%20they%20were%20forced%20to%20come%20together%20to%20challenge%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20hegemony%20in%20Indian%20politics%2C%20the%20INDIA%20parties%20haven%E2%80%99t%20missed%20a%20chance%20to%20highlight%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20authoritarianism%2C%20overreach%20and%20disrespect%20towards%20the%20constitution%20and%20political%20conventions%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAhead%20of%20the%20Mumbai%20meeting%2C%20former%20Maharashtra%20chief%20minister%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20articulated%20a%20similar%20sentiment.%20He%20said%20he%20would%20prefer%20INDIA%20to%20be%20called%20a%20grouping%20to%20safeguard%20%E2%80%9CBharat%20Mata%E2%80%9D%20against%20an%20authoritarian%20regime%20instead%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Copposition%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20all%20of%20us%20are%20of%20different%20ideologies.%20But%20our%20aim%20is%20to%20safeguard%20the%20Constitution%E2%80%A6%20We%20are%20here%20to%20safeguard%20democracy.%20We%20will%20not%20let%20any%20dictator%20chain%20Bharat%20Mata.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20political%20necessity%20of%20INDIA%20has%20been%20amply%20clear%20from%20the%20multiple%20statements%20of%20opposition%20leaders.%20With%20concrete%20steps%20being%20taken%20in%20states%20where%20its%20constituents%20are%20ruling%2C%20the%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20political%20campaign%20is%20also%20gradually%20becoming%20clearer%20by%20the%20day.%20The%20INDIA%20campaign%20may%20not%20just%20hinge%20upon%20mounting%20a%20critique%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20on%20its%20apparent%20failures%20in%20generating%20sufficient%20employment%20or%20containing%20the%20price%20rise%20of%20essential%20commodities%20or%20its%20alleged%20autocratic%20excesses.%20But%20it%20is%20also%20likely%20to%20hold%20out%20concrete%20promises%20and%20a%20development%20vision%20for%20the%20electorate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Mumbai%20meeting%20is%20likely%20to%20iron%20out%20many%20of%20these%20issues.%20A%2011-member%20committee%20and%20various%20subcommittees%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20formed%2C%20which%20will%20be%20steered%20by%20a%20president%20and%20a%20convenor.%20By%20how%20the%20events%20have%20shaped%20up%20in%20the%20last%20few%20months%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%20are%20frontrunners%20for%20the%20positions%2C%20although%20many%20in%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20are%20also%20said%20to%20be%20aspirants.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20of%20the%20contentious%20issues%20are%20also%20likely%20to%20be%20discussed%20in%20the%20Mumbai%20meeting.%20The%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20and%20the%20Congress%20will%20have%20to%20resolve%20their%20differences%2C%20while%20the%20Left%20parties%20and%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20will%20also%20have%20to%20sort%20out%20an%20arrangement%20to%20be%20less%20hostile%20towards%20each%20other.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20INDIA%20leaders%20have%20also%20advocated%20having%20a%20common%20symbol%20for%20the%20alliance%20for%20a%20common%20campaign.%20The%20committees%20that%20will%20be%20formed%20will%20chalk%20out%20a%20common%20minimum%20programme%20and%20a%20campaign%20strategy%20that%20will%20be%20taken%20up%20nationally.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20senior%20most%20leader%20of%20INDIA%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20tackling%20a%20rebellion%20in%20his%20party%2C%20has%20said%20that%20two%20more%20parties%20will%20join%20the%20alliance%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20taking%20the%20total%20tally%20of%20parties%20to%2028.%20Seat-sharing%20talks%20will%20most%20likely%20be%20postponed%20as%20of%20now.%20However%2C%20the%20Mumbai%20meeting%20will%20set%20the%20parties%20off%20towards%20the%20finish%20line%2C%20their%20first%20challenge%20being%20the%20upcoming%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693441834000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F18155503%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-18-at-1.20.10-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fat-indias-mumbai-meet-seat-sharing-to-take-back-seat-as-focus-is-on-common-programme-vision%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bihar%20caste%20census%20and%20the%20'Gruha%20Lakshmi'%20universal%20cash%20benefit%20programme%20for%20women-headed%20households%20in%20Karnataka%20are%20two%20examples%20of%20the%20kind%20of%20policies%20the%20combined%20opposition%20is%20looking%20at%20in%20its%20quest%20to%20offer%20the%20electorate%20a%20real%20alternative%20to%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fat-indias-mumbai-meet-seat-sharing-to-take-back-seat-as-focus-is-on-common-programme-vision%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20told%20NY%20officials%20he%20was%20too%20busy%20saving%20the%20world%20'from%20nuclear%20holocaust'%20to%20commit%20business%20fraud%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Trump%2C%20Kim%20Jong%20Un%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63567918ffcac3001876e68a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20North%20Korea's%20leader%20Kim%20Jong-un%20talk%20before%20a%20meeting%20in%20the%20Demilitarized%20Zone(DMZ)%20on%20June%2030%2C%202019%2C%20in%20Panm