holocaust%20if%20I%20didn't%20deal%20with%20North%20Korea.%20I%20think%20you%20would%20have%20a%20nuclear%20war%2C%20if%20I%20weren't%20elected%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20of%20his%20four%20years%20in%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20think%20you%20might%20have%20a%20nuclear%20war%20now%20if%20you%20want%20to%20know%20the%20truth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20made%20these%20assertions%20while%20distancing%20himself%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fletitia-james-trump-tower-files-court-battle-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estate%20attorney%20general's%20claims%20that%20over%20the%20past%20decade%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20his%20New%20York-based%20real%20estate%20company%2C%20the%20Trump%20Organization%2C%20routinely%20misstated%20the%20value%20of%20its%20assets%20to%20save%20money%20on%20bank%20loans%2C%20insurance%2C%20and%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20at%20least%202011%2C%20the%20company%20inflated%20the%20worth%20of%20its%20assets%20by%20anywhere%20from%20%24800%20million%20to%20%242%20billion%20in%20a%20single%20year%2C%20the%20attorney%20general's%20office%20alleged%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20newly-released%20transcript%2C%20Trump%20swore%20to%20the%20AG's%20office%20in%20his%20April%20deposition%20that%20he's%20had%20%26quot%3Bvirtually%26quot%3B%20no%20role%20in%20his%20company%20since%20his%20first%20run%20for%20president%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20son%20Eric%20is%20much%20more%20involved%20with%20it%20than%20I%20am%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20testified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20doing%20other%20things.%20And%20I%20guess%20you%20could%20say%20on%20something%20major%2C%20whatever.%20But%20I've%20been%20much%20less%20involved%20in%20it%20than%20%E2%80%94%20over%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20five%20or%20six%20years%20than%20ever%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20own%20deposition%2C%20taken%20in%20March%2C%20Eric%20Trump%20agreed%20that%20his%20father%20stepped%20away%20years%20ago%20from%20the%20day-to-day%20operations%20of%20the%20company%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F23932456-ag-deposition-eric-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20a%20transcript%20also%20made%20public%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Trump%20administration%2C%20Donald%20Trump's%20assets%20within%20the%20Trump%20Organization%20were%20transferred%20to%20a%20trust%20controlled%20by%20Eric%20Trump%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20Jr.%2C%20and%20Allen%20Weisselberg%2C%20the%20company's%20chief%20financial%20officer%20at%20the%20time.%20The%20elder%20Trump%20was%20%26quot%3Bfocused%20on%20doing%20something%20much%20larger%20than%20the%20Trump%20Organization%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20time%2C%20Eric%20Trump%20said%20in%20his%20deposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20leaving%20the%20presidency%20in%20January%202021%2C%20Trump%20has%20been%20technically%20%26quot%3Bat%20the%20top%20of%20the%20pyramid%26quot%3B%20but%20has%20only%20involved%20himself%20in%20passion%20projects%20within%20the%20Trump%20Organization%2C%20Eric%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20he%20involved%20in%20the%2C%20you%20know%2C%20in%20the%20day-to-day%20operations%20of%20the%20organization%3F%20He%20might%20be%20involved%20in%20something%20that%20he%20cares%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20Eric%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20president%20has%20been%20particularly%20interested%20in%20the%20greenery%20on%20his%20golf%20courses%2C%20Eric%20Trump%20testified.%20Otherwise%2C%20he%20has%20left%20his%20two%20eldest%20sons%20and%20other%20executives%20to%20run%20the%20company%2C%20Eric%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20he's%20at%20one%20of%20the%20golf%20courses%20and%20he%20wants%20to%20redesign%20a%20green%20or%20something%20like%20that%20because%20he's%20golf%20fanatic%20and%20loves%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Eric%20Trump%20said%20in%20the%20deposition.%