l%20to%20her%20lawsuit's%20allegations.%20In%20it%2C%20she%20argues%20that%20the%20Trump%20Organization's%20annual%20financial%20filings%20reduced%20his%20actual%20net%20worth%20by%20anywhere%20from%2017%25%20to%2039%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20value%20of%20the%20company's%20assets%20was%20off%20by%20anywhere%20from%20%24812%20million%20to%20%242.2%20billion%20in%20a%20single%20year%2C%20she%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawyers%20for%20the%20Trump%20defendants%20will%20have%20the%20chance%20to%20rebut%20the%20attorney%20general's%20summary%20judgment%20request%20in%20response%20papers%20and%20in%20oral%20arguments%20scheduled%20for%20September%2022.%20They%20have%20repeatedly%20denied%20wrongdoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20took%20a%20shot%20at%20President%20Biden%20early%20on%20in%20his%20deposition%2C%20the%20transcript%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20Biden%2C%20he%20certainly%20does%20business%20and%20politics%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20But%20I%20felt%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20legitimate%20President%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20not%20mix%20business%20and%20politics%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20virtually%20not%20involved%20at%20all%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20company%20from%202015%20on%2C%20Trump%20told%20the%20attorney%20general's%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20rarely%20have%20anything%20to%20do%20with%20anything%20having%20to%20do%20with%20the%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wasn't%20%E2%80%94%20I%20really%20wasn't%20interested%2C%20believe%20it%20or%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20of%20running%20his%20company%20since%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20interested%20in%20solving%20the%20problem%20with%20North%20Korea%2C%20which%20was%20ready%20to%20blow%20up%2C%20and%20solving%20the%20problems%20we%20had%20with%20China%2C%20who%20was%20just%20ripping%20us%20off%20left%20and%20right%2C%20and%20making%20sure%20that%20Russia%20never%20went%20into%20Ukraine%2C%20whi