%20view%20of%20India.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20medians%20of%2034%25%20and%2016%25%20had%20unfavourable%20and%20no%20views%20on%20India%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EData%20from%20a%20survey%20Pew%20conducted%20in%2019%20countries%20last%20year%20says%20that%20a%20median%20of%2028%25%20of%20people%20said%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20influence%20in%20the%20world%20was%20getting%20stronger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20those%2019%20countries%2C%20respondents%20were%20most%20inclined%20to%20say%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20influence%20had%20not%20changed%20much%20in%20recent%20years%20(48%25%20median)%2C%20but%20only%2019%25%20of%20Indians%20agree%20with%20this%20view%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pew%20said%20in%20its%20latest%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fglobal%2F2023%2F08%2F29%2Fviews-of-india-lean-positive-across-23-countries%2Fpg_2023-08-29_views-of-india_00-02%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fglobal%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2023%2F08%2FPG_2023.08.29_views-of-india_00-02.png%3Fw%3D528%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%20countries%20Pew%20conducted%20surveys%20in%20this%20year%2C%20respondents%20from%20Israel%20had%20the%20most%20positive%20views%20on%20India%2C%20with%2071%25%20of%20the%20respondents%20registering%20a%20favourable%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPew%20added%20that%20Israelis%20with%20right-wing%20political%20beliefs%20reported%20more%20positive%20views%20on%20India%20than%20Israelis%20on%20the%20left%20side%20of%20the%20spectrum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%2051%25%20of%20the%20respondents%20had%20a%20positive%20view%20on%20India.%20However%2C%20liberals%20were%2010%20percentage%20points%20more%20likely%20than%20their%20conservative%20counterparts%20to%20view%20India%20favourably.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fglobal%2F2023%2F08%2F29%2Finternational-views-of-india-and-modi%2Fpg_2023-08-29_views-of-india_01-02%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fglobal%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2023%2F08%2FPG_2023.08.29_views-of-india_01-02.png%3Fw%3D640%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20think%20tank%20has%20also%20found%20that%20while%20India%20is%20generally%20viewed%20favourably%20by%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20%E2%80%93%20including%20by%20residents%20of%20G20%20countries%2C%20delegations%20from%20which%20India%20will%20host%20next%20week%20in%20New%20Delhi%20%E2%80%93%20residents%20of%20some%20European%20countries%20and%20of%20South%20Africa%20see%20India%20less%20positively%20than%20they%20did%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAcross%20these%20select%20countries%2C%20views%20of%20India%20have%20generally%20become%20more%20negative%20since%20the%20question%20was%20last%20asked%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pew%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20observed%20the%20opposite%20phenomenon%20in%20Mexico%20and%20Nigeria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fglobal%2F2023%2F08%2F29%2Finternational-views-of-india-and-modi%2Fpg_2023-08-29_views-of-india_01-03%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fglobal%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2023%2F08%2FPG_2023.08.29_views-of-india_01-03.png%3Fw%3D640%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20found%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20viewed%20less%20favourably%20by%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20than%20India%20as%20a%20country.%3Cb%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22bold%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3EA%20median%20of%2040%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20that%20they%20did%20not%20have%20confidence%20in%20Modi%20to%20do%20the%20right%20thing%20regarding%20world%20affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPew%20did%20not%20ask%20European%20respondents%20about%20their%20confidence%20in%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20respondents%2C%20though%2C%20feel%20very%20confidently%20about%20their%20prime%20minister.%20Seventy-nine%20percent%20of%20Indians%20who%20were%20polled%20by%20Pew%20on%20their%20opinion%20of%20Modi%20reported%20a%20favourable%20view%2C%20with%2055%25%20of%20all%20Indians%20saying%20they%20had%20a%20%E2%80%98very%20favourable%E2%80%99%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%2020%25%20of%20Indian%20respondents%20had%20an%20overall%20unfavourable%20view%20of%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fglobal%2F2023%2F08%2F29%2Finternational-views-of-india-and-modi%2Fpg_2023-08-29_views-of-india_01-04%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fglobal%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2023%2F08%2FPG_2023.08.29_views-of-india_01-04.png%3Fw%3D640%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fglobal%2F2023%2F08%2F29%2Findians-views-of-modi-and-other-national-leaders%2Fpg_2023-08-29_views-of-india_02-01%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fglobal%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2023%2F08%2FPG_2023.08.29_views-of-india_02-01.png%3Fw%3D640%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPew%20said%20that%20young%20adults%20from%20India%20were%20more%20likely%20than%20older%20respondents%20to%20answer%20its%20questions%20on%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20both%20of%20whom%20along%20with%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20do%20not%20command%20%E2%80%98very%20favourable%E2%80%99%20views%20as%20the%20prime%20minister%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20regarding%20Indian%20respondents%2C%20the%20think%20tank%20also%20found%20that%20men%20were%20more%20likely%20than%20their%20female%20counterparts%20to%20believe%20that%20India%20was%20becoming%20a%20stronger%20force%20in%20the%20world%2C%20although%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20two%20in%20terms%20of%20percentage%20points%20(71%25%20and%2065%25%20respectively)%20is%20not%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fglobal%2F2023%2F08%2F29%2Findians-views-of-india%2Fpg_2023-08-29_views-of-india_03-01%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fglobal%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2023%2F08%2FPG_2023.08.29_views-of-india_03-01.png%3Fw%3D640%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThirty%20thousand%20people%20across%2024%20countries%20took%20part%20in%20Pew%E2%80%99s%20latest%20survey%2C%20which%20was%20conducted%20between%20February%20and%20March%20this%20year%2C%20Reuters%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Findia-viewed-favourably-most-g20-members-modis-image-divided-survey-2023-08-29%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693409518000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F24092024%2FFwz9N5AaEAYUoVS.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fpew-research-finds-indians-more-confident-of-country-than-rest-of-world%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%2079%25%20of%20Indians%20feel%20favourably%20about%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20a%20median%20of%2040%25%20of%20respondents%20from%2019%20countries%20other%20than%20India%20do%20not%20have%20confidence%20in%20Modi's%20foreign%20policy%2C%20finds%20a%20Pew%20survey.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fpew-research-finds-indians-more-confident-of-country-than-rest-of-world%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Three%20key%20areas%20where%20drones%20have%20allowed%20Ukraine%20to%20take%20the%20initiative%20over%20Russia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693406520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F08%2F70x70%2Fskynews-drone-strike-russian-warplane_6268126.jpg%3F20230830173240%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fukraine-war-three-key-areas-where-drones-have-allowed-zelenskyys-forces-to-